.005339324,-0.026659487,0.012168272,-0.031277355,-0.0028766475,0.015879093,0.014108692,0.012602376,-0.0050887032,0.017014366,-0.029221619,0.00492121,0.0036866753,0.010576588,-0.017321063,-0.023981502,0.011898577,0.006022755,0.03681481,0.0012010346,0.016458714,-0.02225732,0.010017576,0.0055445987,0.024318354,-0.0034767203,-0.023787672,-0.005970054,0.01270035,0.018039031,-0.03209127,0.013683095,-0.0045057936,-0.013872952,0.012348279,0.012761172,0.027961904]","categories":[],"created_at":"2026-03-31T04:53:45.599387+00:00","updated_at":"2026-04-23T05:25:10.23463+00:00","description":"ยกระดับเครื่องประดับของคุณให้เป็นประสบการณ์ระดับพรีเมียม ด้วยภาพแพ็กเกจจิ้ง ที่ออกแบบจากสิ่งที่คุณมี เพื่อสะท้อนความหรูหรา คุณค่า และเรื่องราวของแบรนด์","format_tags":["image"],"is_official":true,"industry_tags":[],"selling_price":2100,"thumbnail_url":"https://yonnvlhgwdxkuirhdfaz.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-thumb-8695fa01-504f-4264-9b9d-fb142a2da29a.png?t=1775032698600","use_case_tags":[],"creator_payout":360,"current_version":1,"markup_multiplier":7,"contribution_margin":1800,"performance_bonus_percent":0,"markup_multiplier_override":null},{"id":"7acfeaf1-5637-4346-af0f-ac15b47669f5","name":"Stationery Packshot","tags":[],"status":"published","user_id":"d873b284-c192-45a2-af86-c2314e7c7ce8","api_cost":300,"category":"Photography","keywords":[],"settings":{"graph":{"edges":[{"id":"xy-edge__f2e7f926-b47c-4c03-99f9-8900f25b8cf7default-1660f305-cbfe-47de-93b9-9c0cfbedefabref_image","source":"f2e7f926-b47c-4c03-99f9-8900f25b8cf7","target":"1660f305-cbfe-47de-93b9-9c0cfbedefab","sourceHandle":"default","targetHandle":"ref_image"},{"id":"xy-edge__1660f305-cbfe-47de-93b9-9c0cfbedefabimage-73b094d7-3a6f-4ce6-9faf-29fe1ac0a97fdefault","source":"1660f305-cbfe-47de-93b9-9c0cfbedefab","target":"73b094d7-3a6f-4ce6-9faf-29fe1ac0a97f","sourceHandle":"image","targetHandle":"default"}],"nodes":[{"id":"1660f305-cbfe-47de-93b9-9c0cfbedefab","data":{"label":"Banana Pro (Image Gen)","params":{"model":"nano-banana-pro","prompt":"Create a high-end commercial marketing campaign visual centered on the uploaded pen product, maintaining perfect visual consistency and brand integrity at all times. Aspect ratio 3:4, ultra high resolution, photorealistic, commercial production quality.\n\nBefore designing the scene, visually analyze the pen: identify it as a precision writing instrument used for technical drawing and detailed illustration; determine its real-world usage context (professional sketching, drafting, line art creation); extract its dominant and secondary color palette directly from the barrel, grip, clip, and branding; identify its materials (matte or gloss plastic, brushed metal, lacquered finish, rubber grip, metallic tip); and define its brand personality (precision-driven, technical, premium craftsmanship, modern, minimal, engineering-focused). All creative and artistic decisions must be derived strictly from this analysis. Do not introduce unrelated objects. All elements must logically support the pen’s function.\n\nDevelop a cohesive luxury advertising concept showing the pen actively drawing a sharp, precise mechanical line illustration of a Gundam-style mecha model on clean white technical drawing paper. Capture the pen tip mid-stroke, with dense black ink flowing cleanly onto the paper surface. The partially completed mecha line art should appear highly technical, symmetrical, and sharply defined, emphasizing crisp geometry and mechanical detailing. No random decorative props. Only relevant elements such as high-quality drawing paper and subtle drafting realism are allowed.\n\nCompose a bold hero shot where the pen is dominant and centered in an elegant action still-life composition. Maintain strong negative space and clear separation between the pen and background. Include realistic grounding shadows from the pen onto the paper. No floating effect unless physically justified. The pen must remain 100% accurate in shape, proportion, logo, typography, color, and material finish. No distortion, no warping, no redesign, no geometry alteration.\n\nInclude extreme macro detail highlighting the metallic tip precision, the exact moment ink meets paper, micro paper fiber texture, razor-sharp line quality, and the surface finish and typography on the pen barrel. Emphasize hyper-realistic micro contrast and ultra-sharp focus at the point of contact.\n\nCreate a tactile sensory close-up that emphasizes realistic pressure interaction between pen and paper, subtle indentation from the nib, rich ink saturation, and controlled line thickness. No exaggerated ink splashes or fantasy effects—keep physics believable and grounded.\n\nDesign the lighting and background environment inspired strictly by the pen’s color palette. Use harmonized tones and a refined, modern gradient that complements the pen body without overpowering it. Soft, controllable studio lighting with a sculptural key light defining the pen form, subtle rim highlights on the metal tip, realistic shadows across the paper, high dynamic range, and luxury advertising-grade post-processing. The final image should feel modern, sophisticated, precise, cinematic, aspirational, and suitable for premium brand websites, social media hero visuals, digital billboards, and luxury e-commerce platforms.","edit_instruction":""},"exposed":{}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":435,"y":420}},{"id":"f2e7f926-b47c-4c03-99f9-8900f25b8cf7","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","nodeName":"Image Upload","required":true,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"Upload your image"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":150,"y":525}},{"id":"73b094d7-3a6f-4ce6-9faf-29fe1ac0a97f","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":780,"y":525}}]},"example_inputs":["https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-example-i