-banana-pro","prompt":"Create asuitable for high-end commercial marketing campaigns centered on the product to be uploaded.\n\n a unique visual concept while maintaining the perfect consistency \n\nA bold, iconic still life hero shot\n\nExtreme macro detail highlighting material, surface, or texture\n\nSensory close-up emphasizing tactile and realistic qualities\n\nColor-driven conceptual scene inspired by the product's color palette\n\nVisual Rules:\n\nThe product must remain 100% accurate in terms of shape, proportion, label, font, color, and brand identity.\n\nThe product must not be distorted, warped, or redesigned.\n\nClear separation between the product and the background.\n\nLighting & Style:\n\nSoft, controllable studio lighting\n\nSubtle highlights, realistic shadows\n\nHigh dynamic range, ultra-sharp focus\n\nLuxury advertising aesthetic in editing\n\nHigh-end sensory marketing look\n\nOverall Feel:\n\nModern, sophisticated, visually harmonious and unified\n\nHigh-end commercial promotional campaign\n\nDesigned specifically for brand websites, social media platforms, and digital billboards\n\ncinematic, exquisite, and aspirational\n\n3:4 aspect ratio","aspect_ratio":"3:4","edit_instruction":""},"exposed":{}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":15,"y":315}},{"id":"66b4d9b7-b8b8-4f25-97f8-19b4ac4248a4","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":360,"y":405}}]},"example_inputs":["https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-example-input-d03f355f-5d43-4c54-8916-8659a1097b63-1775460967718-0.jpg?t=1775460968430"],"preview_images":["https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-preview-d03f355f-5d43-4c54-8916-8659a1097b63-1775196936953-0.png?t=1775196938565","https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-b