g dark, Brown stone prop placed subtly behind the bottle to add depth. Background is a rich, moody, dark gradient surface. Lighting is dramatic, controlled overhead studio lighting that casts soft, defined highlights on the glass bottle and sharpens the label clarity, with gradual, realistic shadow falloff. The focus is ultra-sharp on the product, showcasing every texture and detail. The overall atmosphere is premium and powerful. Ultra-realistic, 8K detail. Do not change the shape, packaging, label, logo, or color. Keep composition clean, balanced, and premium.","model_name":"nano-banana-pro","aspect_ratio":"3:4"},"exposed":{}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":255,"y":270}},{"id":"f923c3fe-53f6-41bc-88c7-63772e092623","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","nodeName":"Image Upload","required":true,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"Upload your image"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":-90,"y":495}},{"id":"89815d6f-2a57-4cad-bb5f-f769aa2036a4","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":675,"y":495}},{"id":"7fdbf147-c0f4-4bb0-84c7-cca899debca5","data":{"label":"Banana Pro (Image Gen)","params":{"prompt":"Close-up shot of a man spraying perfume on his neck.\nOnly his neck to his chest is visible.\nHe's wearing a navy blue shirt, unbuttoned at the top.\nHe's holding a bottle with the logo uncovered.\n\nThe image's color tone is similar to the reference image.","model_name":"nano-banana-pro","aspect_ratio":"3:4"},"exposed":{}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":660,"y":795}},{"id":"82cf1400-9408-4b40-993e-45b265276c80","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":1005,"y":480}}]},"example_inputs":["https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-example-input-469065b7-1a2f-42b7-b37d-b7b13e1081c1-1775549028693-0.jpg?t=1775549030045","https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/publi