otography","keywords":[],"settings":{"graph":{"edges":[{"id":"xy-edge__95c6df41-a56f-4b53-aec8-7bf91948277bdefault-a43d3c1d-6b46-4688-a530-66eaa6d4f558ref_image","source":"95c6df41-a56f-4b53-aec8-7bf91948277b","target":"a43d3c1d-6b46-4688-a530-66eaa6d4f558","sourceHandle":"default","targetHandle":"ref_image"},{"id":"xy-edge__d3b6a824-2a95-4455-9d32-6e69cd706647default-a43d3c1d-6b46-4688-a530-66eaa6d4f558ref_image","source":"d3b6a824-2a95-4455-9d32-6e69cd706647","target":"a43d3c1d-6b46-4688-a530-66eaa6d4f558","sourceHandle":"default","targetHandle":"ref_image"},{"id":"xy-edge__a43d3c1d-6b46-4688-a530-66eaa6d4f558image-d71004f0-1384-4777-8a4a-88efdee9f673default","source":"a43d3c1d-6b46-4688-a530-66eaa6d4f558","target":"d71004f0-1384-4777-8a4a-88efdee9f673","sourceHandle":"image","targetHandle":"default"}],"nodes":[{"id":"a43d3c1d-6b46-4688-a530-66eaa6d4f558","data":{"label":"Banana Pro (Image Gen)","params":{"prompt":"Use the ring from @[Image Upload](95c6df41-a56f-4b53-aec8-7bf91948277b)  as the main subject, and match the underwater mood, lighting, and composition style of @[Creator Image](d3b6a824-2a95-4455-9d32-6e69cd706647) . A high-end macro underwater product shot: the ring has just dropped into clear water, releasing fresh streams of tiny bubbles and a soft splash trail around it. Soft-contrast film look, clean pastel colors with a light blue tint, luminous highlights, gentle grain, and a dreamy cinematic atmosphere. Shallow depth of field with razor-sharp focus on the ring and gemstone reflections; background smoothly blurred.\r\n\r\nThe bottom is covered with multicolored pebbles arranged in depth, receding into the distance; include prominent foreground rocks at the lower-left and lower-right corners framing the scene. Ultra high resolution, crisp micro-details on metal and stone facets, realistic refraction and caustics, natural underwater haze, no harsh contrast, no oversaturation.","model_name":"nano-banana-pro","aspect_ratio":"3:4"},"exposed":{}},"type