rly visible but not exaggerated.\n\nClean, simple background in a refined neutral tone. Premium fashion beauty campaign aesthetic.\n\nNegative Prompt\n\nDo not change gender.\nDo not alter face shape.\nNo cross-eyes.\nNo blurry eyes.\nDo not look directly into the camera.\nNo big smile.\nNo heavy makeup.\nNo plastic-looking skin.\nNo diamond jewelry.\nNo gold jewelry.\nNo logos.\nNo text.\nNo deformed hands.\nNo extra fingers.\nNo twisted wrists.\nNo blur.\nNo cropped-out jewelry.\n\nRecommended Settings\nAspect ratio: 4:5 or 3:4\nHigh resolution\nCFG / Prompt strength: medium\nIdentity strength: medium-high\nComposition strength: high\nUse a fixed seed for easier iteration and tuning\nRefine Pass\n\n(If your workflow has a detail refinement node)\n\nIncrease the shine and sharpness of the silver jewelry\nRefine the fingers and bracelet edges\nReduce skin highlights to keep them natural\nMaintain a soft fashion-beauty tone","model_name":"nano-banana-pro","aspect_ratio":"Auto"},"exposed":{"aspect_ratio":true}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":150,"y":375}},{"id":"e8e4a3cb-1b10-4c5f-8ef4-d8e2a5fd52a6","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","nodeName":"นายแบบ นางแบบ","required":true,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"นายแบบ นางแบบ"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":-150,"y":90}},{"id":"dbfa4df5-0095-4cea-be92-7d1b6bfed2a9","data":{"label":"Creator Image","accept":"image/*","fileName":"freepik_photo-a-20yearold-white-male-with-curly-brown-hair-wearing-a-black-jacket-and-silver-jewelry-posing-against-a-pink-background_0003.png","nodeName":"Creator Image","required":true,"fieldType":"image","uploading":false,"fieldLabel":"Upload your image","previewUrl":"https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/sign/ai-media/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/a2b6af66-2c25-4200-966a-5cb888ab40ee.png?token=eyJraWQiOiJzdG9yYWdlLXVybC1zaWduaW5nLWtleV9jM2VkYzBhMy1jMDIyLTQyOTgtODIxMS1mMTc5YTA1ZDUxN2IiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJhaS1tZWRpYS9mYjRkZTdlMi0