ttle. The product is centered in the lower-middle area, sharply readable, with a clean premium editorial beauty composition.\r\n\r\nImportant:\r\n- Preserve the uploaded product packaging faithfully.\r\n- Keep the brand/logo/text consistent with the original packaging.\r\n- Do not distort the bottle proportions.\r\n- Do not invent a different label design.\r\n- The bottle must stand on a glossy black lacquered studio surface.\r\n- Show a subtle realistic dark reflection beneath the product.\r\n- Do not place the bottle on glass, a transparent surface, or the model’s arm or body.\r\n- The supporting surface should feel like a premium black beauty campaign set, not a normal table.\r\n- Do not place the bottle on the model’s arm, hand, or body.\r\n- Show a subtle realistic reflection beneath the product.\r\n- Make the result feel like a real premium skincare ad shot for Instagram, Facebook, TikTok, and brand campaigns.\r\n- Clean, tasteful, elegant, expensive, Asian beauty aesthetic.\n\nLighting: soft studio beauty lighting with controlled highlights on the skin, subtle rim light, premium glow, cinematic contrast, clean reflections on the packaging, smooth shadows, polished luxury commercial photography.\n\nBackground: dark elegant studio background in deep navy, charcoal, or cool-toned luxury gradient, minimal and clean, helping the product and skin stand out. Overall mood should feel premium, modern, feminine, and editorial.\n\nStyle: ultra-realistic, photorealistic, luxury skincare advertisement, high-end beauty campaign, glossy magazine quality, social-media-ready, commercially usable, premium retouched finish while keeping natural skin texture.\n\nCamera: close-up portrait beauty shot, 85mm lens look, shallow depth of field, sharp focus on the product and model’s face, luxury commercial composition.\n\nImportant:\n\n- Preserve the uploaded product packaging faithfully.\n\n- Keep the brand/logo/text consistent with the original packaging.\n\n- Do not distort the bottle proportions.\n\n- Do not invent a different label design.\n\n- Make the result feel like a real premium skincare ad shot for Instagram, Facebook, TikTok, and brand campaigns.\n\n- Clean, tasteful, elegant, expensive, Asian beauty aesthetic.","model_name":"nano-banana-2","aspect_ratio":"3:4"},"exposed":{}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":255,"y":165}},{"id":"c9bd9836-eee6-43cf-9350-b02cb093b727","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":615,"y":165}}]},"example_inputs":["https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-example-input-9888fb68-4af3-4e1d-92d1-4131bbe43c50-1775385930487-0.png?t=1775385932031","https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-example-input-9888fb68-4af3-4e1d-92d1-4131bbe43c50-1775385932031-1.png?t=1775385933170"],"preview_images":["https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-preview-9888fb68-4af3-4e1d-92d1-4131bbe43c50-1775391051421-0.png?t=1775391053017","https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-preview-9888fb68-4af3-4e1d-92d1-4131bbe43c50-1775391060134-0.png?t=1775391061728","https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-preview-9888fb68-4af3-4e1d-92d1-4131bbe43c50-1775391070210-0.png?t=1775391072525"],"setup_instructions":"อัปโหลดภาพแพ็กเกจสกินแคร์ของคุณให้ชัดเจน \"หากมีนางแบบสามารถอัพโหลดเพื่อใช้นางแบบที่คุณต้องการได้\" ระบบจะนำสินค้าไปสร้างเป็นภาพโฆษณาแบบพรีเมียม โดยมีนางแบบลุคสวยดูแพงจัดองค์ประกอบร่วมกับสินค้าในสไตล์งานบิวตี้แคมเปญ เหมาะสำหรับใช้โปรโมตแบรนด์บน Instagram, Facebook, TikTok และสื่อออนไลน์ต่างๆ"},"base_cost":300,"embedding":"[-0.019446604,0.02318089,-0.0012058563,-0.09527498