nA sophisticated luxury café table scene photographed in a clean editorial style. Show three beautifully styled drinks arranged on a round light-colored table, similar to a premium specialty café menu photoshoot. Each drink should be presented in elegant high-end glassware, with a refined, expensive look. The drinks should feel visually distinct from each other while still belonging to the same luxurious café brand universe.\r\n\r\nDrink styling:\r\nDecorate each drink beautifully and naturally based on its flavor and ingredients. Add tasteful garnish, creamy foam, textured toppings, coffee layers, syrup drips, ice cubes, fruit accents, herbs, coconut flakes, vanilla cream, citrus peel, chocolate dust, caramel drizzle, edible flowers, or other elegant details where appropriate. Every glass should look appetizing, premium, artistic, and professionally styled. Keep the drink designs realistic but elevated like a café signature menu.\r\n\r\nMood and environment:\r\nLuxury café atmosphere, warm natural sunlight, soft shadows, rich creamy highlights, expensive lifestyle feeling, calm and elegant composition, premium coffeehouse aesthetic, airy but refined. Add tasteful props such as a small ceramic milk pitcher, a gold spoon, a wooden coaster, a book, or soft blurred plants in the background, but keep the drinks as the hero. Background should feel minimal, classy, and softly blurred.\r\n\r\nVisual direction:\r\nPhotorealistic beverage photography, editorial café styling, premium glass textures, realistic condensation, soft reflections, layered liquids, beautiful foam, realistic ice, subtle highlights, clean composition, natural depth of field, warm beige and brown tones, upscale boutique café mood.\r\n\r\nLayout:\r\nVertical composition, balanced spacing, drinks clearly visible, logo centered at the top, no clutter, no busy background, no excessive props.\r\n\r\nImportant:\r\nDo not add any text, menu labels, drink names, prices, captions, headlines, or extra typography anywhere in the image.\r\nOnly the provided shop logo may appear at the top center.\r\nNo watermark, no poster text, no promotional text, no random letters.\r\n\r\nThe final result should look like a luxury morning drinks campaign photo for a premium café brand.","model_name":"nano-banana-pro","aspect_ratio":"Auto"},"exposed":{"aspect_ratio":true}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":435,"y":375}},{"id":"e0b2e082-26f0-4146-8dc7-e1fb8def460c","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Drink 1","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"เครื่องดื่ม 1 ของคุณ คือ (ตัวอย่าง Matcha Late)","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":90,"y":120}},{"id":"ba49c0a2-cc6b-44bb-9412-1c4d978e6ede","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Drink 2","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"เครื่องดื่ม 2 ของคุณ คือ (ตัวอย่าง Caramel Macchiato)","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":372.7285712705174,"y":119.22258270006667}},{"id":"e3a0fe40-f092-46c4-9c5b-cdb62f45daae","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Drink 3","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"เครื่องดื่ม 3 ของคุณ คือ (ตัวอย่าง Chocolate Milk Cream on top)","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":660,"y":120}},{"id":"caec48dd-d2ad-4f8f-ba74-166ea80f2ff6","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","nodeName":"logo Upload","required":true,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"อัพโหลดโลโก้ของคุณ"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":90,"y":375}},{"id":"9efce56d-dcb5-400d-a293-a84b2bc621c9","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":810,"y":375}}]},"example_inputs":[],"preview_images":["https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-preview-6f916f2c-e8b2-4c26-82e3-f0074919aea1-1775729135269-0.jpg?t=1775729135894","https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-