r framing similar to the reference\r\n- large custom Thai typography composition placed in the upper area above the dish\r\n- balanced negative space between typography and plate\r\n- minimal, elegant, premium editorial layout\r\n\r\nFood requirements:\r\n- replace the original dish with the uploaded food image\r\n- preserve the exact identity of the uploaded dish\r\n- do not redesign or reinterpret it into another menu\r\n- keep the real ingredients, colors, textures, proportions, and recognizable appearance of the uploaded dish\r\n- restage the food naturally into a premium plated presentation inspired by the reference\r\n- if the uploaded dish includes sauce, garnish, vegetables, or side elements, they may be arranged neatly only if supported by the uploaded image\r\n- make the food look realistic, appetizing, premium, and professionally photographed\r\n- preserve realistic gloss, moisture, fibers, crispness, sauce sheen, char, and natural shadow detail\r\n- do not oversmooth the food\r\n- do not make it look fake or plastic\r\n\r\nTypography concept:\r\n- replace all existing text in the reference with a completely new Thai typography composition\r\n- use Thai language only for all visible text unless the user explicitly inputs another language\r\n- design the typography from scratch as bespoke Thai composition typography, not a normal font overlay\r\n- create a new custom typographic arrangement every time based on the exact input words\r\n- redesign the letterforms, spacing, line breaks, proportions, rhythm, hierarchy, and graphic balance based on the actual Thai text\r\n- adapt the typography visually to the word length, tone, and mood of the input\r\n- typography should feel art-directed, editorial, elegant, premium, and custom-made for the given phrase\r\n- the main text should feel like a custom Thai wordmark\r\n- the secondary text should feel like a refined supporting line\r\n- allow subtle custom Thai letterform styling such as expanded spacing, tall proportions, ligature-like flow, stroke contrast, overlap, nesting, or refined inline/detail work when appropriate\r\n- keep the typography readable and professionally typeset in correct Thai\r\n- prioritize correct Thai spelling, correct Thai glyph construction, and natural Thai reading flow\r\n- do not generate fake Thai glyphs\r\n- do not make the typography look like generic stock fonts\r\n- do not imitate the original Latin letters; instead reinterpret the same premium editorial feeling in Thai\r\n\r\nText content:\r\n- Main text: #[ข้อความหลัก](e59088b4-541b-444a-a017-98be2d7deab6) \r\n- Secondary text: #[ข้อความรอง](8d083256-b096-4ec8-a49f-8c47fc59c0df) \r\n\r\nTypography layout rules:\r\n- place the main Thai title in the upper center area as the dominant typographic element\r\n- place the secondary Thai line below the main title in a smaller elegant style\r\n- redesign the composition each time according to the exact input text\r\n- do not copy the original text layout literally\r\n- preserve only the premium editorial hierarchy and spacing feel\r\n- keep the typography visually integrated with the plate, background, and negative space\r\n- composition should feel calm, sophisticated, balanced, and poster-like\r\n\r\nTypography styling direction:\r\n- custom Thai editorial display typography\r\n- luxurious, airy, refined, and modern\r\n- elegant restaurant-poster composition\r\n- bespoke Thai lettering based on the exact words provided\r\n- main text may be wide, elegant, spaced out, tall, contrast-led, or delicately stylized as appropriate to the phrase\r\n- secondary text should be smaller, softer, and supportive while still clearly readable\r\n- use soft white or warm-white typography tones that harmonize with the muted dark background\r\n- no cheap effects\r\n- no bevel\r\n- no random decorative swashes unless naturally justified by the Thai words\r\n- no English placeholder text\r\n- no Latin-looking Thai\r\n\r\nLighting and mood requirements:\r\n- match the reference image’s calm premium editorial mood\r\n- soft natural directional light across the plate and table\r\n- subtle shadow falloff and gentle highlight transitions\r\n- slightly moody but clean atmosphere\r\n- keep the food well lit and appetizing\r\n- overall tone should feel elegant, modern, warm, and sophisticated\r\n\r\nImportant constraints:\r\n- render only the exact text provided in the input fields\r\n- do not add extra text\r\n- do not change spelling\r\n- do not invent subtitles\r\n- remove all original reference text completely\r\n- no watermark\r\n- no logo unless explicitly provided\r\n- no extra dishes\r\n- no unrelated props\r\n- no messy layout\r\n- no distorted plate or food\r\n- no unreadable typography\r\n- no placeholder English text\r\n\r\nStyle direction:\r\npremium Thai editorial food poster, bespoke Thai composition typography, elegant restaurant campaign visual, minimal luxury plating, custom type-led poster design\n","model_name":"nano-banana-2","aspect_ratio":"3:4"},"exposed":{"prompt":false}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":360,"y":300}},{"id":"544b9a33-9692-4379-b39a-c0b779bba707","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":750,"y":510}},{"id":"8fb2c46b-e1f4-4c70-ad65-c7f70218ec42","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","config":{"example_image_urls":[]},"nodeName":"อาหาร1","required":true,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"อาหาร"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":45,"y":810}},{"id":"e59088b4-541b-444a-a017-98be2d7deab6","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"ข้อความหลัก","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"ข้อความหลัก","isRequired":true,"exampleText":"NEW MENU","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":-270,"y":195}},{"id":"21c01ffd-5ef5-4fb7-bba2-d6b8cd4693be","data":{"label":"Creator Image","accept":"image/*","fileName":"5102524d05464df6661580057337bbec.jpg","nodeName":"Creator Image","required":true,"fieldType":"image","uploading":false,"