und, cucumber slices on the right, and a dried red chili in the foreground.\r\n\r\nReplace the original meatballs with meatballs based on @[Image Upload](8d42150b-995d-4ae3-97c4-00322ef74d6e) . The meatballs must closely match @[Image Upload](8d42150b-995d-4ae3-97c4-00322ef74d6e)  in shape, form, texture, and overall appearance, while keeping the same skewer layout, portion, placement, and visual balance as @[Creator Image](364adde6-858d-4488-9a1c-af77cd5cbe8b) . Each skewer must contain meatballs of the same shape and same type only. Do not mix different shapes or types on the same skewer. Coat the meatballs with glossy spicy red sauce and garnish with finely chopped green herbs.\r\n\r\nPlace @[โลโก้](498a0ea6-c6b3-4b7f-9505-a8c512802adc)  centered at the top in a small, clean size with a small top margin. Keep the logo’s original shape, color, details, and text. Do not redesign or distort it.\r\n\r\nThe final image should be a realistic premium food photograph with sharp focus on the skewers and a slightly blurred background.\n","model_name":"nano-banana-pro","aspect_ratio":"1:1"},"exposed":{"aspect_ratio":true}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":300,"y":240}},{"id":"364adde6-858d-4488-9a1c-af77cd5cbe8b","data":{"label":"Creator Image","accept":"image/*","fileName":"mediaforge-31c4b822-521a-4867-83f2-c2fd578021e1-1.jpg","nodeName":"Creator Image","required":true,"fieldType":"image","uploading":false,"fieldLabel":"Upload your image","previewUrl":"https://yonnvlhgwdxkuirhdfaz.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/sign/ai-media/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/ab0c78c5-506a-4f70-b52d-26a38e4ed18d.jpg?token=eyJraWQiOiJzdG9yYWdlLXVybC1zaWduaW5nLWtleV80OGRhM2Y3NS1jOTEzLTRmOGItOTA5My1mNzU1NWY0ZDY1YTYiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJhaS1tZWRpYS9mYjRkZTdlMi05ZjZlLTQ1OWItYmIxYi00NjRmNmFlMTRiZWEvYWIwYzc4YzUtNTA2YS00ZjcwLWI1MmQtMjZhMzhlNGVkMThkLmpwZyIsImlhdCI6MTc3NjkxNzM0NywiZXhwIjoxNzc3MDAzNzQ3fQ.468EbeLhHKxlQYw2XPRmBc9W45iCqe1WVUbhWuSi4Ds","storagePath":"fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b