lished professional hero shot while keeping it faithful to the uploaded image and menu name.\r\n\r\nTransform it into a premium professional dessert hero shot.\r\n\r\nCreate an elegant, refined, appetizing dessert photography result with premium café or patisserie character: beautiful cream texture, delicate layers, glossy glaze, chocolate detail, fruit freshness, soft crumbs, syrup shine, or pastry texture depending on the dessert. The dessert must remain the main subject and look like an elevated professional version of the same item, not a different recipe.\r\n\r\nStyle the image like a luxury dessert advertisement or premium menu hero image. Use graceful composition, flattering studio-quality lighting, refined shadows, realistic dessert texture, and a clean upscale café atmosphere. Add tasteful dessert visual cues only when naturally appropriate, such as marble surfaces, ceramic plates, glass elements, linen, or soft neutral-to-pastel backgrounds, but keep the frame clean and focused on the dessert.\r\n\r\nUse a camera angle that feels ideal for hero presentation: a slightly angled close-up or a 45-degree food photography perspective depending on the dessert. Emphasize softness, shine, detail, elegance, and irresistible premium texture. Keep the image highly realistic, polished, commercially usable, and beautiful.\r\n\r\nDo not add text, logos, watermarks, extra unrelated desserts, unrealistic garnish, collage layout, or human hands. Avoid changing the dessert into another menu item. Preserve realism and authentic dessert appeal.","model_name":"nano-banana-pro","aspect_ratio":"Auto"},"exposed":{"aspect_ratio":true}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":180,"y":165}},{"id":"319e1075-dd14-4e00-9dcc-047e1da687cf","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":780,"y":165}},{"id":"2eb35c85-2e1c-459b-9ed9-69455cd359e2","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Menu name","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"เมนูของคุณคืออะไร","placeholder