3419c2)  for the identity of the beef steak, including the cut style, thickness, meat texture, grill marks, surface character, color tone, portion identity, and the restaurant’s unique product appearance. Preserve the recognizable identity of the steak from @[อัปโหลดสเต็กเนื้อของคุณ](159e0b07-17c0-4d24-b30b-a94d453419c2)  and do not turn it into a generic steak.\r\n\r\nAutomatically adapt the camera angle based on the plate and food arrangement from @[Creator Image](2bf1b389-87d1-473a-aa38-ced741abff9a) . If the plate is wide, flat, or spread out, use a slightly top-down or 45-degree angle. If the steak is thicker, layered, or arranged with more height, use a 3/4 angle to emphasize depth, volume, and meat texture. Choose the most appetizing and natural hero angle according to @[Creator Image](2bf1b389-87d1-473a-aa38-ced741abff9a) .\r\n\r\nArrange the beef steak naturally and beautifully within the plate, following the composition style of @[Creator Image](2bf1b389-87d1-473a-aa38-ced741abff9a) . Make the dish look balanced, premium, and visually complete, without looking too crowded or too empty. Ensure the steak and side elements sit harmoniously on the plate.\r\n\r\nThe beef steak must look glossy, juicy, succulent, and freshly cooked. Enhance the surface texture so the meat looks moist and rich, with an appetizing shine. Add a glossy sauce coating over the steak so the sauce lightly covers the meat with a mouthwatering sheen. Emphasize rich texture detail, juicy meat fibers, and a hot freshly served appearance.\r\n\r\nPreserve the unique identity of the restaurant’s steak from @[อัปโหลดสเต็กเนื้อของคุณ](159e0b07-17c0-4d24-b30b-a94d453419c2) . Do not replace its signature characteristics. You may enhance the texture, moisture, and sauce finish to make it look more premium, juicy, and visually appetizing, but it must still remain faithful to @[อัปโหลดสเต็กเนื้อของคุณ](159e0b07-17c0-4d24-b30b-a94d453419c2) .\r\n\r\nUse realistic premium food photography styling with professional lighting, appetizing highlights, natural shadows, detailed texture, and strong focus on the steak. Keep the final image suitable for a restaurant menu, food advertisement, or delivery platform hero image.\r\n\r\nDo not change the composition direction away from @[Creator Image](2bf1b389-87d1-473a-aa38-ced741abff9a) .\r\nDo not lose the steak identity from @[อัปโหลดสเต็กเนื้อของคุณ](159e0b07-17c0-4d24-b30b-a94d453419c2) .\r\nDo not add unrelated ingredients or props that distract from the main dish.\r\nAdd only minimal garnish or side details if they naturally support the presentation.\r\n\r\nStyle: photorealistic, premium food photography, restaurant menu hero shot, juicy glossy beef steak, sauce-coated steak, rich texture, appetizing commercial food image.","model_name":"nano-banana-pro","aspect_ratio":"Auto"},"exposed":{"aspect_ratio":true}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":281.95418317294025,"y":184.17260279006513}},{"id":"159e0b07-17c0-4d24-b30b-a94d453419c2","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","nodeName":"อัปโหลดสเต็กเนื้อของคุณ","required":true,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"อัปโหลดสเต็กเนื้อของคุณ"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":-75,"y":-15}},{"id":"a7a47492-3d1f-494e-a971-524d407cb61a","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":660,"y":360}},{"id":"2bf1b389-87d1-473a-aa38-ced741abff9a","data":{"label":"Creator Image","accept":"image/*","fileName":"freepik_2837580812.png","nodeName":"Creator Image","required":true,"fieldType":"image","uploading":false,"fieldLabel":"Upload your image","previewUrl":"https://yonnvlhgwdxkuirhdfaz.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/sign/ai-media/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/9b213bc3-d2f0-4863-96da-a32e3c0c7d13.png?token=eyJraWQiOiJzdG9yYWdlLXVybC1zaWduaW5nLWtleV80OGRhM2Y3NS1jOTEzLTRmOGItOTA5My1mNzU1NWY0ZDY1YTYiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJhaS1tZWRpYS9mYjRkZTdlMi05ZjZlLTQ1OWItYmIxYi00NjRmNmFlMTRiZWEvOWIyMTNiYzMtZDJmMC00ODYzLTk2ZGEtYTMyZTNjMGM3ZDE