e","targetHandle":"default"}],"nodes":[{"id":"3e855054-8493-4359-8ce7-f3410c5747b6","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","nodeName":"food","required":true,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"Upload your image"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":405,"y":390}},{"id":"fdb02b3d-ca2e-45e2-98b7-d6ac1fd51b44","data":{"label":"Banana Pro (Image Gen)","params":{"prompt":"Use the uploaded food image @@[food](3e855054-8493-4359-8ce7-f3410c5747b6)  as the exact dish reference.\r\n\r\nThe user has identified the dish as: ##[Menu name](debb1dd2-2f99-48b1-9753-3baecdc917ad) \r\nAdditional dish details provided by the user: ##[Optional dish details](284bca8f-88a8-4355-8c74-ef196a039b83) \r\n\r\nTreat the uploaded image and the user-provided dish name as the source of truth. The final result must still clearly represent this specific menu item, not a similar or different dish. Preserve the original dish identity, ingredients, proportions, plating logic, and recognizable appearance from the input image.\r\n\r\nDo not redesign, replace, or reinterpret the dish. Enhance it only into a more polished professional menu-ready packshot while keeping it faithful to the uploaded image and menu name.\r\n\r\nTransform it into a premium professional food menu packshot with hero-shot quality.\r\n\r\nCreate a clean, polished, commercially usable food photography result designed for menus, promotional layouts, delivery platforms, and restaurant branding. The dish must remain the main subject and look like an elevated professional version of the same food, not a different recipe.\r\n\r\nStyle the image like a premium restaurant menu hero image with packshot clarity. Use neat composition, bright controlled studio-quality lighting, realistic food texture, natural food color, soft refined shadow, and a clean premium surface or background that supports easy placement into graphic designs. Keep the image visually strong, but cleaner and more versatile than a dramatic advertisement.\r\n\r\nUse a camera angle that feels ideal for menu presentation: a clean slightly angled close-up or a practical 45-degree food photography perspective depending on the dish. Emphasize clarity, balance, texture, shape, and easy usability for design work. Keep the image highly realistic, polished, commercially usable, and premium.\r\n\r\nDo not add text, logos, watermarks, extra unrelated dishes, unrealistic garnish, collage layout, or human hands. Avoid changing the food into another menu item. Preserve realism and practical menu-ready appeal.","model_name":"nano-banana-pro","aspect_ratio":"Auto"},"exposed":{"aspect_ratio":true}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":720,"y":390}},{"id":"debb1dd2-2f99-48b1-9753-3baecdc917ad","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Menu name","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"เมนูของคุณมีอะไรบ้าง เช่น กะเพราหมูสับไข่ดาว, ผัดซีอิ๊ว, เส้นใหญ่ราดหน้า","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":1065,"y":630}},{"id":"284bca8f-88a8-4355-8c74-ef196a039b83","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Optional dish details","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"รายละเอียดเพิ่มเติม เช่น มีแก้วโค้กเย็นวางข้างๆ, มีเหยือกเบียร์ , บรรยากาศแบบในร้านอาหารริมแม่น้ำ","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":1065,"y":855}},{"id":"b955a052-f16f-4924-a1b9-cfa4c7310ae2","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":1410,"y":405}}]},"example_inputs":[],"preview_images":["https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-preview-e39adbfc-9cbd-4f9b-a51a-17c4109d939f-1775794402851-0.jpg?t=1775794403522","https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-preview-e39adbfc-9cbd-4f9b-a51a-17c4109d939f-1775794403522-1.jpg?t=1775794404870"],"setup_instructions":"อัปโหลดภาพอาหารที่ต้องการ 1 ภาพ (มากกว่า 1 เมนูบนโต๊ะ) โดยควรเป็นภาพที่เห็น