hy lighting with natural shadows, appetizing highlights, and strong focus on the dish.\r\n\r\nDo not change the composition away from @[Creator Image](364adde6-858d-4488-9a1c-af77cd5cbe8b) .\r\nDo not lose the dish identity from @[Image Upload](8d42150b-995d-4ae3-97c4-00322ef74d6e) .\r\nDo not add unrelated props or ingredients.\r\nDo not add any text other than the logo.\r\n\r\nStyle: photorealistic, premium food photography, restaurant menu hero shot, glossy juicy pad kra pao crispy pork, appetizing commercial food image.\n","model_name":"nano-banana-pro","aspect_ratio":"1:1"},"exposed":{"aspect_ratio":false}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":285,"y":75}},{"id":"364adde6-858d-4488-9a1c-af77cd5cbe8b","data":{"label":"Creator Image","accept":"image/*","fileName":"mediaforge-89265d12-408d-4e96-a38f-0ed583de79fe-1.jpg","nodeName":"Creator Image","required":true,"fieldType":"image","uploading":false,"fieldLabel":"Upload your image","previewUrl":"https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/sign/ai-media/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/02b49181-5167-4305-a8fa-c039efdefe16.jpg?token=eyJraWQiOiJzdG9yYWdlLXVybC1zaWduaW5nLWtleV9jM2VkYzBhMy1jMDIyLTQyOTgtODIxMS1mMTc5YTA1ZDUxN2IiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJhaS1tZWRpYS9mYjRkZTdlMi05ZjZlLTQ1OWItYmIxYi00NjRmNmFlMTRiZWEvMDJiNDkxODEtNTE2Ny00MzA1LWE4ZmEtYzAzOWVmZGVmZTE2LmpwZyIsImlhdCI6MTc3Njg1MzUxOCwiZXhwIjoxNzc2OTM5OTE4fQ.rhdI0CEgGOB29d5WKpOF5gPwjnK1P9MpnQseIL5ttjY","storagePath":"fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/02b49181-5167-4305-a8fa-c039efdefe16.jpg","creatorAsset":true},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":-345,"y":15}},{"id":"8d42150b-995d-4ae3-97c4-00322ef74d6e","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","nodeName":"Image Upload","required":true,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"อับโหลดภาพกะเพราของคุณ"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":-45,"y":330}},{"id":"c9502d01-c72a-4a95-828d-316b12c12562","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":735,"y":22