e-input-img2-image-input-img1-image-edit-refer__64227.png","nodeName":"Creator Image","required":true,"fieldType":"image","uploading":false,"fieldLabel":"Upload your image","previewUrl":"https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/sign/ai-media/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/fe60ce24-8209-4013-a754-9a4bf92407cd.png?token=eyJraWQiOiJzdG9yYWdlLXVybC1zaWduaW5nLWtleV9jM2VkYzBhMy1jMDIyLTQyOTgtODIxMS1mMTc5YTA1ZDUxN2IiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJhaS1tZWRpYS9mYjRkZTdlMi05ZjZlLTQ1OWItYmIxYi00NjRmNmFlMTRiZWEvZmU2MGNlMjQtODIwOS00MDEzLWE3NTQtOWE0YmY5MjQwN2NkLnBuZyIsImlhdCI6MTc3NTQ1NTI0OSwiZXhwIjoxNzc1NTQxNjQ5fQ.2w4CSKokqtZ5dKWC2o9JBfePE3HZKlclpilsGY8wjiY","storagePath":"fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/fe60ce24-8209-4013-a754-9a4bf92407cd.png","creatorAsset":true},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":60,"y":510}},{"id":"1e60777c-8183-42fc-99ae-f8ab2eb0f2a6","data":{"label":"Banana Pro (Image Gen)","params":{"prompt":"Image Input (@@[เครื่องประดับ](c0c9b993-58d5-4d6e-bfc3-c43915ae5241)  is the main image) → Image Input (@@[Creator Image](9f96de09-659a-4cfe-b0e7-f4f782124dd0)  is the ring reference) → Image Edit (Reference/Style + Inpaint) → Upscale/Sharpen\r\n\r\nPrompt (Image Edit):\r\n\r\nUse image @@[Creator Image](9f96de09-659a-4cfe-b0e7-f4f782124dd0)  as the reference for all composition and camera angles (circular ripple sand, depth of field, studio lighting like in advertising). Replace the “ring” in the image with the same ring from @@[เครื่องประดับ](c0c9b993-58d5-4d6e-bfc3-c43915ae5241)  in every detail (shape of the setting, criss-cross shank, prongs, blue gemstone, shiny silver metal material). Position the ring in the same location as in image @@[Creator Image](9f96de09-659a-4cfe-b0e7-f4f782124dd0)  and make it “slightly embedded in the sand,” creating realistic indentations and sand grains leaning against the edge of the ring. The contact shadow should be clear. Adjust the “sand color” to match the jewelry tone of @@[เครื่องประดับ](c0c9b993-58d5-4d6e-bfc3-c43915ae5241) , using a cool, luxurious tone (silver-gray/muted blue) with a subtle sparkle, while maintaining the sand texture and ripples of the reference image. Achieve advertising-level sharpness. Metal and gemstone details are clear, clean, and free of distractions.\r\n\r\nNegative Prompt:\r\n\r\nAll text, logos, watermarks, lettering on the ring, text on the image, frames, disproportionate cropping, human hands, other objects, incorrect ring style, discolored gemstones, distortion, blurring, heavy noise, unrealistic shadows.\r\n\r\nMask/Inpaint:\r\n\r\nMask only the area of ​​the “original ring + sand around the ring” to create a new ring and indentations/grains on the sand, while preserving other sand textures and the background from @@[Creator Image](9f96de09-659a-4cfe-b0e7-f4f782124dd0) \r\n\r\nSettings (Recommended):\r\n\r\nStrength/Transform Low-Medium (preserve @@[Creator Image](9f96de09-659a-4cfe-b0e7-f4f782124dd0)  composition), Detail/Quality High, Preserve lighting On, Seed fixed for repeatability.","model_name":"nano-banana-pro","aspect_ratio":"Auto"},"exposed":{}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":375,"y":240}},{"id":"c0c1e703-ce37-4ea1-8724-d6da7cabc193","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":735,"y":285}}]},"example_inputs":["https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-example-input-26d858cc-8572-4c29-99fc-35cb74ca1b90-1775453210622-0.avif?t=1775453211622"],"preview_images":["https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-preview-26d858cc-8572-4c29-99fc-35cb74ca1b90-1775452998759-0.png?t=1775452999614","https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-preview-26d858cc-8572-4c29-99fc-35cb74ca1b90-1775453085386-0.png?t=1775453086180"],"setup_instruct