uired":true,"exampleText":"ย่างเกลือ","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":-270,"y":525}},{"id":"ca54849d-dea0-4e61-ad4c-9813d9d3ac6b","data":{"label":"Banana Pro (Image Gen)","params":{"prompt":"Use the uploaded image @[Creator Image](21c01ffd-5ef5-4fb7-bba2-d6b8cd4693be)  as the composition, mood, framing, lighting, and layout reference only.\r\n\r\nUse the uploaded food image @[อาหาร1](8fb2c46b-e1f4-4c70-ad65-c7f70218ec42)  as the exact food reference.\r\n\r\nCreate a premium editorial-style food poster inspired by the reference image.\r\n\r\nOverall composition:\r\n- one hero food dish placed near the lower center on a table\r\n- soft outdoor lifestyle atmosphere with shallow depth of field\r\n- blurred background garden or patio feeling\r\n- warm sunlight from the upper-right area\r\n- soft fabric curtain hanging from the upper-left side\r\n- weathered table surface in the foreground\r\n- vertical poster framing similar to the reference\r\n- large custom typography composition placed above and around the dish area\r\n- elegant balance between food, sunlight, negative space, and typography\r\n\r\nFood requirements:\r\n- replace the original dish with the uploaded food image\r\n- preserve the exact identity of the uploaded dish\r\n- do not redesign or reinterpret it into another menu\r\n- keep the real ingredients, colors, textures, proportions, and recognizable appearance of the uploaded dish\r\n- restage the food naturally into a premium plated presentation inspired by the reference\r\n- make it look realistic, appetizing, premium, and professionally photographed\r\n- preserve realistic gloss, texture, crispness, moisture, sauce detail, and natural shadows\r\n- do not oversmooth the food\r\n- do not make it look fake or plastic\r\n\r\nTypography concept:\r\n- replace all existing text in the reference with a completely new Thai typography composition\r\n- use Thai language only for all visible text unless the user explicitly inputs another language\r\n- design the typography from scratch as a custom Thai display type composition, not a standard font overlay\r\n- the typography must feel art directed, editorial, premium, and visually integrated with the layout\r\n- redesign the letterforms, proportions, line breaks, spacing, and graphic rhythm based on the exact input words\r\n- adapt the typography composition to the length, shape, and meaning of each input phrase\r\n- allow expressive Thai letterform styling, contrast, curves, ligatures, stroke variation, scale contrast, overlap, and composition play\r\n- typography should look like a bespoke poster title design, not a simple typed caption\r\n- prioritize correct Thai spelling and readability\r\n- keep the design visually bold but still readable\r\n- do not transliterate Thai into English-looking forms\r\n- do not use random Latin letters\r\n\r\nText content:\r\n- Main text: #[ข้อความหลัก](e59088b4-541b-444a-a017-98be2d7deab6) \r\n- Secondary text 1: #[ข้อความรอง](8d083256-b096-4ec8-a49f-8c47fc59c0df)  \r\n\r\n\r\nTypography layout rules:\r\n- create a layered Thai typographic composition above the food, similar in visual impact to the reference\r\n- use dynamic size contrast between the main text and supporting text\r\n- let the main text become the visual hero of the poster together with the food\r\n- secondary lines may wrap, tuck in, overlap, curve, extend, or interlock naturally depending on the actual Thai words\r\n- the layout must be recomposed each time according to the input text, not copied from the reference literally\r\n- keep the overall composition premium, balanced, and poster-like\r\n- the typography should feel custom-designed specifically for the given words\r\n\r\nTypography styling direction:\r\n- modern Thai editorial display typography\r\n- elegant, premium, artistic, and distinctive\r\n- custom composition typography, not template text\r\n- refined high-end poster aesthetic\r\n- use white or near-white typography similar in visual weight to the reference\r\n- subtle depth, clean edges, and strong readability\r\n- no cheap decorative effects\r\n- no stock-font look\r\n\r\nLighting and mood requirements:\r\n- match the reference image’s warm natural sunlight mood\r\n- soft bright highlight from the upper-right\r\n- premium outdoor editorial atmosphere\r\n- natural shadow depth on the table and dish\r\n- gentle dreamy blur in the background\r\n- overall tone should feel calm, stylish, premium, and visually sophisticated\r\n\r\nImportant constraints:\r\n- render only the exact text provided in the input fields\r\n- do not add extra text\r\n- do not change spelling\r\n- do not invent subtitles\r\n- do not keep any of the original reference text\r\n- no watermark\r\n- no logo unless explicitly provided\r\n- no extra dishes\r\n- no unrelated props\r\n- no messy layout\r\n- no distorted food\r\n- no unreadable typography\r\n- no English placeholder text\r\n- no random letters or fake Thai glyphs\r\n\r\nStyle direction:\r\npremium Thai editorial food poster, custom Thai display typography, artistic composition typography, elegant outdoor food campaign, high-end restaurant poster, bespoke type-led visual design","model_name":"nano-banana-2","aspect_ratio":"3:4"},"exposed":{}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":360,"y":300}},{"id":"544b9a33-9692-4379-b39a-c0b779bba707","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":750,"y":510}},{"id":"8fb2c46b-e1f4-4c70-ad65-c7f70218ec42","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","config":{"example_image_urls":["https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/flow-assets/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/4034648d-aae9-4eb4-bd7a-7eac3c40cbae.jpg"]},"nodeName":"อาหาร1","required":true,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"อาหาร"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":45,"y":810}},{"id":"e59088b4-541b-444a-a017-98be2d7deab6","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"ข้อความหลัก","textValue