"textInputNode","position":{"x":-270,"y":-135}},{"id":"a79a0cc5-2262-4b51-81a4-e5620e36570a","data":{"label":"Creator Image","accept":"image/*","fileName":"98f86f1815c6c944d91cf47a537e1027.jpg","nodeName":"ต้นแบบ","required":true,"fieldType":"image","uploading":false,"fieldLabel":"ต้นแบบ","previewUrl":"https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/sign/ai-media/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/d5855739-6e31-41ba-9110-fa2d503a00f5.jpg?token=eyJraWQiOiJzdG9yYWdlLXVybC1zaWduaW5nLWtleV9jM2VkYzBhMy1jMDIyLTQyOTgtODIxMS1mMTc5YTA1ZDUxN2IiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJhaS1tZWRpYS9mYjRkZTdlMi05ZjZlLTQ1OWItYmIxYi00NjRmNmFlMTRiZWEvZDU4NTU3MzktNmUzMS00MWJhLTkxMTAtZmEyZDUwM2EwMGY1LmpwZyIsImlhdCI6MTc3NjQxMzEyOCwiZXhwIjoxNzc2NDk5NTI4fQ.1bL72Qfd6j2gpPm4rqyPGNdIBavbGMx3-eXQJ4CQ1hc","storagePath":"fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/d5855739-6e31-41ba-9110-fa2d503a00f5.jpg","creatorAsset":true},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":15,"y":285}},{"id":"ca54849d-dea0-4e61-ad4c-9813d9d3ac6b","data":{"label":"Banana Pro (Image Gen)","params":{"prompt":"Create a premium restaurant menu poster inspired by elegant editorial food photography, using the uploaded dish images as the exact food references.@@[ต้นแบบ](a79a0cc5-2262-4b51-81a4-e5620e36570a) \r\n\r\r\nUse these uploaded images as the source dishes:\r\n- แก้ว 1 = @@[แก้ว1](8fb2c46b-e1f4-4c70-ad65-c7f70218ec42) \r\n- แก้ว 2 = @@[แก้ว2](c93734e5-6703-4646-8207-4a63d6ef5a02) \r\n\r\n\r\nText to display in the image:\r\n\r\nMain title at the top:\r\n\"#[หัวข้อ](e59088b4-541b-444a-a017-98be2d7deab6)\"\r\n\r\nDish 1 text:\r\nTop line: ##[เฮด1](6d2bc958-1d4f-40a2-8c83-362860ce1050) \r\n\r\n\r\nDish 2 text:\r\nTop line: ##[เฮด2](2c21e7d4-f9d4-4566-ba7c-441f5f9e4b09) \r\n\r\n\r\r\nImportant food handling rules:\r\nTreat each uploaded dish image as the exact food reference. Preserve the original identity of each dish, including its real ingredients, plating logic, shape, texture, color, portion, and recognizable appearance. Do not redesign the food into another dish. Do not replace ingredients. Do not add unrelated toppings or decorations.\r\n\r\nYou may professionally restyle the presentation only by:\r\n- rearranging the composition\r\n- adjusting the plate position\r\n- changing the camera angle slightly\r\n- refining the perspective\r\n- improving the lighting and shadows\r\n- making the food look more polished and appetizing\r\n\r\nVery important:\r\nAfter placing the uploaded food dishes into the composition, adjust each dish’s angle, plate direction, and camera perspective so the overall layout feels balanced, natural, and visually premium, while still keeping the food itself faithful to the uploaded image.\r\nThe food can be re-shot from a slightly new angle for better composition, but it must still clearly match the original uploaded dish.\r\nMatch the lighting direction, shadow behavior, mood, and warmth of the reference style: warm direct light, realistic shadows, rich wooden tones, elegant restaurant atmosphere.\r\n\r\nVisual style:\r\n- premium restaurant editorial poster\r\n- warm wooden wall background\r\n- rich brown wooden table surface\r\n- cozy upscale dining mood\r\n- direct warm lighting with realistic contrast\r\n- realistic shadows and depth\r\n- clean, minimal, elegant composition\r\n- commercial-quality food styling\r\n- appetizing but realistic texture\r\n- no overly artificial CGI look\r\n\r\nTypography and text layout:\r\n- Show the main title \"\" at the top in large elegant Thai typography.\r\n- Place each dish label near its corresponding dish.\r\n- Each dish label must have 2 lines:\r\n  - top line = smaller supporting text\r\n\r- Add subtle curved pointer marks or elegant hand-drawn arrow accents pointing to each dish, similar to a premium editorial menu layout.\r\n- Text color should be white or soft warm white for readability.\r\n- Keep all text clean, premium, and well-spaced.\r\n\r\nComposition rules:\r\n- If the number of dishes is 1:\r\n  show only Dish 1 as the hero dish, large and beautifully centered, with strong negative space and one text label.\r\n- If the number of dishes is 2:\r\n  show only Dish 1 and Dish 2, arranged in a balanced editorial composition with pleasing depth and spacing. One dish may sit slightly forward and the other slightly behind.\r\n- If the number of dishes is 3:\r\n  show Dish 1, Dish 2,  in a refined recommendation-poster layout, with one hero dish in the foreground and the other two supporting dishes naturally placed around it.\r\n\r\nDo not show any extra dishes beyond the selected number.\r\nDo not display any text other than:\r\n- the main title \"##[หัวข้อ](e59088b4-541b-444a-a017-98be2d7deab6) \"\r\n- the provided dish texts for each selected dish\r\n\r\nFinal result requirements:\r\nThe final image must look like a polished restaurant promotional poster that is realistic, appetizing, elegant, warm, balanced, and ready for menu marketing or social media promotion.","model_name":"nano-banana-2","aspect_ratio":"3:4"},"exposed":{}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":300,"y":285}},{"id":"544b9a33-9692-4379-b39a-c0b779bba707","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":615,"y":285}},{"id":"8fb2c46b-e1f4-4c70-ad65-c7f70218ec42","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","nodeName":"แก้ว1","required":true,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"ภาพเครื่องดื่มแก้วที่ 2"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":600,"y":-270}},{"id":"c93734e5-6703-4646-8207-4a63d6ef5a02","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","nodeName":"แก้ว2","required":true,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"ภาพเครื่องดื่มแก้วที่ 1"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":285,"y":-255}},{"id":"2c21e7d4-f9d4-4566-ba7c-441f5f9e4b09","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"เฮดไลน์2","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"ข้อความของแก้วที่ 2","isRequired":true,"exampleText":"เช่น ชื่อเมนู","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":15,"y":-135}},{"id"