bf714273)  an important part of the composition. The surface should support the food presentation without overpowering the dishes. Keep the overall image clean, realistic, visually balanced, and easy to look at.\r\n\r\nIf the user requests a clean white table, make the background bright, minimal, and uncluttered. If no table surface or background style is provided, use a clean white table surface by default.\r\n\r\nKeep the image highly realistic, organized, premium, and commercially usable for social media, sharing sets, and menu promotions.\r\n\r\nDo not add text, logos, watermarks, or unrelated dishes. Preserve realism and premium flat lay appeal.","model_name":"nano-banana-pro","aspect_ratio":"Auto"},"exposed":{"aspect_ratio":true}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":660,"y":405}},{"id":"4b86df97-c53a-49f3-a92f-bfdbf8b5986c","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","nodeName":"2","required":true,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"ภาพอาหารของคุณ 2"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":-600,"y":705}},{"id":"a5b66f05-3ceb-4ccb-b2e8-2c46e835c793","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","nodeName":"3","required":true,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"ภาพอาหารของคุณ 3"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":-600,"y":225}},{"id":"e54d3fa9-c701-4ccf-9db6-647240593096","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","nodeName":"4","required":false,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"ภาพอาหารของคุณ 4"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":-30,"y":705}},{"id":"19f3ebc3-e64c-47f8-8872-b15504c1fcdc","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","nodeName":"5","required":false,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"5ภาพอาหารของคุณ 5"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":-315,"y":705}},{"id":"71ce2e78-4164-4dd8-8b79-66cb62690410","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","nodeName":"6","required":false,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"ภาพอาหารของคุณ 6"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":-315,"y":210}},{"id":"e473e41b-5bf8-4095-bdfb-53fbe3be0bcb","data":