rence style of the sample image.\r\n\r\nComposition style:\r\n- Vertical poster layout\r\n- Dark black background with dramatic contrast\r\n- A realistic human hand entering from the upper right area, holding a spoon and sprinkling seasoning or spice powder downward\r\n- The uploaded food dish placed prominently in the lower center area as the hero subject\r\n- Cinematic restaurant-style lighting with strong focus on the dish\r\n- Natural shadows, realistic highlights, appetizing texture\r\n- Shallow depth of field, premium food photography look\r\n- The food should feel rich, hot, intense, and highly tempting\r\n- If needed, adjust the plating angle, crop, and perspective of the uploaded food so it fits naturally into the composition while still preserving the original dish identity\r\n- Relight the uploaded food image so its lighting, shadow direction, contrast, and atmosphere match the reference poster style\r\n- Keep the final result realistic and commercially usable\r\n\r\nFood fidelity rules:\r\n- Treat the uploaded food image as the source of truth\r\n- Preserve the real identity of the dish, ingredients, color, texture, structure, and recognizable appearance\r\n- Do not replace the food with another dish\r\n- Do not redesign the dish into a different menu item\r\n- Enhance only the presentation, lighting, and composition so it matches the premium poster style\r\n\r\nText layout rules:\r\n- Place the text on the upper-left side in a stacked vertical layout similar to the reference style\r\n- Each line must appear as a separate text block\r\n- Render EXACTLY the same number of text lines provided in #[Text Lines]\r\n- Do not add extra lines\r\n- Do not remove any provided lines\r\n- Do not invent words\r\n- If the user provides 2 lines, show exactly 2 lines\r\n- If the user provides 3 lines, show exactly 3 lines\r\n- If the user provides 4 lines, show exactly 4 lines\r\n- Every text line must have EXACTLY the same visible text width from the first character edge to the last character edge\r\n- Adjust font size per line as needed so that all lines end up with the same final text width\r\n- The left edge of the visible letters must align perfectly on one vertical line\r\n- The right edge of the visible letters must align perfectly on one vertical line\r\n- This means every line must start and end at the exact same horizontal positions\r\n- Keep equal padding before and after the text block so the text stack looks perfectly uniform\r\n- Do not add extra words, symbols, or spacing to fake the width\r\n- Do not stretch letters unnaturally\r\n- Only change font size if needed to make each line match the exact same width\r\n- Keep the typography bold, clean, modern, and highly legible\r\n- Use a minimal monochrome or muted light-gray text style that fits the dark premium poster look\nCritical text rule:\r\n- All text lines must be fitted to one identical text-width template, so every line has the exact same left boundary and exact same right boundary.\nMake every text line occupy the EXACT SAME final width. The first visible character of every line must start at the same vertical axis, and the last visible character of every line must end at the same vertical axis. Resize each line independently until all lines match exactly.\n\r\nImportant:\r\n- The uploaded food must remain the hero of the image\r\n- The seasoning sprinkle should visually enhance the dish and feel naturally related to the food\r\n- Make the lighting of every uploaded food input consistent with the reference mood\r\n- No extra objects that distract from the food\r\n- No random text\r\n- No watermark\r\n- No brand logo unless provided by the user","model_name":"nano-banana-2","aspect_ratio":"9:16"},"exposed":{}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":570,"y":-105}},{"id":"b9269143-53bd-4570-91ac-888b529ba506","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"บันทัด2","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"บรรทัด2","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","posit