pired by the uploaded reference image @@[Creator Image](21c01ffd-5ef5-4fb7-bba2-d6b8cd4693be) , using the uploaded food image and uploaded drink image as the exact product references.\r\n\r\nUse these uploaded images as the source items:\r\n- Food = @@[อาหาร](8fb2c46b-e1f4-4c70-ad65-c7f70218ec42) \r\n- Drink = @@[เครื่องดื่ม](c93734e5-6703-4646-8207-4a63d6ef5a02) \r\n\r\nText to display in the image:\r\n\r\nMain headline:\r\n#[เฮดไลน์](e59088b4-541b-444a-a017-98be2d7deab6)\r\n\r\nSubheadline directly below the main headline:\r\n#[ซับ1](8d083256-b096-4ec8-a49f-8c47fc59c0df)\r\n\r\nPromotion / price box text:\r\n#[โปรโมชั่น หรือ ราคา](5fd58986-9328-48f9-9cd3-017af5cf873a)\r\n\r\nImportant product handling rules:\r\nTreat the uploaded food image and uploaded drink image as the exact visual references. Preserve the real identity of both items, including ingredients, shape, texture, portion, color, glassware or plate style, and recognizable appearance. Do not redesign them into different items. Do not replace ingredients. Do not add unrelated toppings, decorations, or extra dishes.\r\n\r\nYou may professionally refine the presentation only by:\r\n- adjusting composition\r\n- changing object placement\r\n- slightly refining camera angle\r\n- improving lighting and shadows\r\n- enhancing realism and appetizing appearance\r\n- making the final composition feel more polished and premium\r\n\r\nVery important:\r\nAfter placing the uploaded food and drink into the final composition, adjust their angle, direction, and camera perspective so the poster feels visually balanced and natural, while still keeping both items faithful to the uploaded images.\r\nThe food and drink may appear re-shot from a slightly better angle for composition, but they must still clearly match the originals.\r\n\r\nReference-style direction:\r\nFollow the visual language of the uploaded reference image:\r\n- warm café or restaurant promotional poster\r\n- cozy upscale atmosphere\r\n- rich brown wooden table\r\n- warm neutral or textured wall background\r\n- direct warm lighting\r\n- realistic shadows and depth\r\n- appetizing editorial food photography\r\n- premium but approachable commercial poster look\r\n- clean composition with strong readability\r\n- realistic textures\r\n- no CGI or over-stylized artificial look\r\n\r\nComposition:\r\n- Show 1 food dish and 1 drink only\r\n- Arrange them as a balanced combo set, similar to a café or restaurant promotion poster\r\n- One item may sit slightly forward and the other slightly behind, but both must remain clearly visible\r\n- Leave enough negative space for the headline and price box\r\n- Make the overall layout feel premium, warm, and naturally appetizing\r\n\r\nTypography and text layout:\r\n- Show the main headline large and prominent near the top area\r\n- Place the subheadline directly below it in a smaller size\r\n- Show one clear promotion / price box that stands out strongly, inspired by restaurant combo posters\r\n- Text should be highly readable, using white, warm white, cream, yellow, red, or brand-appropriate tones that fit the reference style\r\n- Keep typography clean, commercial, and well-spaced\r\n- Do not generate extra text\r\n- Do not paraphrase, translate, or rewrite any input text\r\n- Show only the exact provided text\r\n\r\nDo not display any text other than:\r\n#[เฮดไลน์](e59088b4-541b-444a-a017-98be2d7deab6)\r\n#[ซับ1](8d083256-b096-4ec8-a49f-8c47fc59c0df) \r\n#[โปรโมชั่น หรือ ราคา](5fd58986-9328-48f9-9cd3-017af5cf873a) \r\n\r\nFinal result requirements:\r\nThe final image must look like a polished restaurant combo promotional poster inspired by the uploaded reference image, with one food item and one drink item, warm realistic lighting, elegant composition, strong commercial appeal, and ready for menu marketing or social media promotion.","model_name":"nano-banana-2","aspect_ratio":"3:4"},"exposed":{}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":360,"y":300}},{"id":"544b9a33-9692-4379-b39a-c0b