f31b8-222d-46a0-bb1c-35dd4f6bfcd0","target":"ca54849d-dea0-4e61-ad4c-9813d9d3ac6b","sourceHandle":"default","targetHandle":"ref_image"}],"nodes":[{"id":"8d083256-b096-4ec8-a49f-8c47fc59c0df","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"ข้อความรอง","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"ข้อความรอง","isRequired":true,"placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":-270,"y":525}},{"id":"ca54849d-dea0-4e61-ad4c-9813d9d3ac6b","data":{"label":"Banana Pro (Image Gen)","params":{"prompt":"Create a premium restaurant advertising poster inspired by elegant editorial food photography and upscale fine-dining branding.@@[Creator Image](21c01ffd-5ef5-4fb7-bba2-d6b8cd4693be) \r\n\r\nUse the uploaded food image @@[อาหาร1](8fb2c46b-e1f4-4c70-ad65-c7f70218ec42)  as the exact food reference.\r\nUse the uploaded drink image @@[อาหาร2](c93734e5-6703-4646-8207-4a63d6ef5a02)  as the exact drink reference.\r\nUse the uploaded logo @@[โลโก้](a32f31b8-222d-46a0-bb1c-35dd4f6bfcd0)  as the exact logo reference.\r\n\r\nThe final image must clearly preserve the identity of the uploaded food and drink. Do not replace them with different menu items. Keep the recognizable form, ingredients, proportions, colors, and overall appearance faithful to the input images, while refining them into a more polished luxury restaurant presentation.\r\n\r\nScene and composition:\r\n- Vertical poster composition\r\n- A warm, intimate, high-end restaurant atmosphere\r\n- Deep moody cinematic lighting with elegant highlights and realistic shadows\r\n- Dark polished wooden table in the foreground\r\n- Luxurious tufted velvet sofa or upholstered seating in the background\r\n- Premium editorial plating and realistic restaurant presentation\r\n- Food plate positioned prominently on the lower right or center-right\r\n- Drink glass positioned on the left side, balanced with the plate\r\n- Composition should feel refined, calm, expensive, and romantic\r\n- Background softly blurred but still recognizable as an upscale interior\r\n- Realistic reflections on glass and table surface\r\n- Rich warm tones with subtle green, brown, amber, and golden highlights\r\n\r\nTypography and branding:\r\n- Place the uploaded logo @@[โลโก้](a32f31b8-222d-46a0-bb1c-35dd4f6bfcd0)  at the top center\r\n- Place the main headline text below the logo: #[ข้อความหลัก](e59088b4-541b-444a-a017-98be2d7deab6) \r\n- Place the subheadline text below the main headline: #[ข้อความรอง](8d083256-b096-4ec8-a49f-8c47fc59c0df) \r\ncluttering the layout\r\n- All text must be editable and clearly rendered\r\n- Use thin, elegant, refined Thai typography with a tall, graceful, luxury look\r\n- Typography should feel premium, minimal, airy, and high-end\r\n- Use delicate Thai letterforms with clean spacing and balanced alignment\r\n- Do not use thick, playful, rounded, cartoon, or casual fonts\r\n- Text color should be soft white, ivory, or warm light beige depending on contrast\r\n- Keep the text centered and visually balanced with the logo\r\n- Do not add any extra text beyond the provided inputs\r\n\r\nStyling rules:\r\n- Keep the overall design clean and premium\r\n- Avoid clutter, excessive props, or busy decorations\r\n- Make the food look appetizing and realistic with natural texture\r\n- Make the drink look realistic, elegant, and premium\r\n- Match lighting and perspective between all elements naturally\r\n- Preserve a luxury editorial restaurant-poster feeling\r\n- Final result must look like a professionally art-directed restaurant campaign poster\r\n\r\nImportant:\r\n- Do not invent extra dishes or extra drinks\r\n- Do not change the logo design\r\n- Do not add random English text\r\n- Do not distort Thai text\r\n- Render only the exact provided text inputs\r\n- Ensure all text is readable, elegant, and consistent with luxury restaurant branding","model_name":"nano-banana-2","aspect_ratio":"3:4"},"exposed":{}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":360,"y":300}},{"id":"544b9a33-9692-4379-b39a-c0b779bb