haracter. Do not redesign, recreate, simplify, restyle, distort, or alter the logo in any way.\r\n\r\nThe logo should remain secondary to the food and the text, and should support the branding without overpowering the main composition. Keep enough safe margin from the top and right edges so the logo does not feel cramped.\r\n\r\nIf no logo is provided, do not add any logo or brand mark.\n\r\n\r\nTreat the uploaded image, the user-provided dish name, and the additional dish details as the source of truth for the food identity and visual direction. The final result must still clearly represent this specific food item, not a similar or different dish. Preserve the original dish identity, ingredients, proportions, plating logic, and recognizable appearance from the input image.\r\n\r\nDo not redesign, replace, or reinterpret the dish. Enhance it only into a more polished promotional food image while keeping it faithful to the uploaded image and menu name.\r\n\r\nRender only the following visible text on the image:\r\n- #[Main text to display on the image](89c5f8f4-7d4c-472e-a51d-62130905713c) \r\n- #[Sub text to display on the image](2577276a-3b2c-4de7-859d-9a50b8970f6c) \r\n\r\nDo not render the menu name or the additional dish details as visible text unless they are exactly the same as the main text or sub text provided by the user.\r\nDo not add any extra text, captions, labels, slogans, menu names, or descriptions beyond the main text and sub text.\r\n\r\nCreate a professional food promotional image where the food remains attractive, realistic, and visually strong, while the main text and sub text are beautifully integrated into the layout as designed graphic elements.\r\n\r\nMake the main text the primary visual headline. Make the sub text smaller and secondary, but still clear and readable. If no sub text is provided, show only the main text.\r\n\r\nText style direction:\r\nUse bold, highly eye-catching promotional typography with thick letterforms, strong contrast, layered outlines, and soft graphic shadows. The text should feel loud, energetic, and commercially powerful, like a high-impact food promotion poster.\r\n\r\nKeep the layout optimized for a short, clear message. Make the composition balanced, attractive, commercially usable, and easy to understand at a glance. Keep enough visual separation between the food and the text so both remain clear and impactful.\r\n\r\nDo not add extra text, unrelated dishes, logos, watermarks, or collage clutter. Keep the final result polished, realistic, and ready for restaurant marketing use.\n","model_name":"nano-banana-2","aspect_ratio":"Auto"},"exposed":{"aspect_ratio":true}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":45,"y":210}},{"id":"437a5682-3587-4b86-a37e-70d2329a6d5c","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"[ชื่อเมนู]","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"ชื่อเมนู","isRequired":true,"exampleText":"ระบุชื่อเมนู เพื่อช่วยให้ระบบเข้าใจว่าอาหารในภาพคืออะไร","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":390,"y":360}},{"id":"89c5f8f4-7d4c-472e-a51d-62130905713c","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Main text to display on the image","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"ข้อความหลัก","isRequired":true,"exampleText":"ระบุข้อความที่ต้องการให้แสดงบนภาพ โดยแนะนำให้ใช้ข้อความสั้น กระชับ และอ่านง่าย","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":675,"y":360}},{"id":"97561492-cf5f-4356-8650-1187b259b373","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"[รายละเอียดเพิ่มเติม]","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"รายละเอียดเพิ่มเติม","isRequired":true,"exampleText":"ใส่รายละเอียดเพิ่มเติมได้ เช่น อยากให้ดูร้อนๆ ดูพรีเมียม หรือดูสดใสขึ้น","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":960,"y":360}},{"id":"cfaac851-9c05-4de7-9f0f-3a60cab6de0f","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":1275,"y":195}},{"id":"2577276a-3b2c-4de7-859d-9a50b8970f6c","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Sub text to 