he text side: #[Text Side Background Color](ab131fcc-f249-433f-aa2c-ee19cb81bb1c) \r\nPreferred background color for the food side: #[Food Side Background Color](93aed74d-2ffe-4fbc-923a-154a8167fbb9) \r\nPreferred banner style: #[Banner Style](b6062fc4-0364-4e89-b07b-dc7cd0228a09) \r\nPreferred promo code box style: #[Preferred promo code box style](3a557e3e-9c92-405a-8607-e137dc2d1631) \r\nPreferred text-side position: #[Preferred text-side position](3a112530-980d-43bd-a47d-407f082e0b0e) \r\nPreferred logo position: #[Preferred logo position](36c0f910-816f-4b82-a050-07859c341b21) \r\nPreferred logo size: #[Preferred logo size](50da1d44-4c2a-40d0-bf09-b8437440ab68) \r\n\nLogo to display on the image: @[logo Upload](4e2b2cd2-668c-4829-bf3a-faa7a2f9c87f) \r\n\r\nTreat the uploaded food image and all user-provided text as the source of truth. The final result must clearly represent this specific food item and display the exact text provided by the user. Do not change, rewrite, paraphrase, translate, shorten, or add any extra text.\r\n\r\nCreate a professional food delivery discount banner inspired by a clean split promotional layout with two clearly separated sides. One side must be dedicated to the promotional text and code area, and the other side must prominently feature the uploaded food image as the hero product visual.\r\n\r\nRespect the user's preferred text-side position. If the user chooses left, place the full promotional text layout on the left and the food on the right. If the user chooses right, place the full promotional text layout on the right and the food on the left. Keep the split layout obvious, intentional, and visually balanced.\r\n\r\nDesign the text side as a bold, highly readable promotional panel with strong visual hierarchy:\r\n- ข้อความหัวข้อหลัก is the main headline at the top and should be large and eye-catching.\r\n- โค้ดส่วนลด must appear inside a clear promo-code box based on the requested code-box style.\r\n- ข้อความรับส่วนลดสูงสุด should appear as supporting text near the main discount.\r\n- ข้อความส่วนลดตัวใหญ่ must be the largest and boldest element in the composition.\r\n- รายละเอียดเพิ่มเติม should appear as smaller supporting detail text.\r\n- วันที่เข้าร่วม / เงื่อนไขเวลา should appear as secondary small text for date, participation info, or conditions.\r\n\r\nUse the requested background color for each side and keep the composition clean, bold, modern, and optimized for readability. The food side should feature the uploaded food image beautifully arranged with a polished, appetizing, commercial food-promo look.\r\n\r\nMake the banner feel like a real delivery-app promotion: clear, high-contrast, attractive, modern, and easy to understand at a glance. The food must remain realistic and appetizing, while the text side must remain structured, readable, and visually strong.\r\n\r\nIf a logo is provided, place it cleanly and appropriately according to the requested logo position and size. Preserve the exact original logo identity from the uploaded file, including its layout, colors, proportions, typography, icon shape, and brand character. Do not redesign, recreate, simplify, or alter the logo.\r\n\r\nDo not add unrelated foods, random extra text, watermarks, or collage clutter. Keep the banner polished, professional, realistic, and ready for restaurant marketing use.","model_name":"nano-banana-2","aspect_ratio":"16:9"},"exposed":{}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":210,"y":180}},{"id":"2afe575a-8046-40f6-8411-45f4898c49dc","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Main headline text:","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"ข้อความหัวเรื่องหลักด้านบน","isRequired":true,"exampleText":"เช่น แจกโค้ด ลดคุ้ม!","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":-180,"y":690}},{"id":"700a37a5-13d5-4053-a85e-aee5c96e6e21","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Promo code text","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"โค้ดส่วนลด","isRequired":true,"exampleText":"โค้ดโปรโมชันที่ต้องการแสดงในช่