lar to the reference\r\n- large custom typography composition placed in the upper area above the dish\r\n- balanced negative space between the text and the food\r\n- minimal, luxurious, and editorial layout\r\n\r\nFood requirements:\r\n- replace the original dish with the uploaded food image\r\n- preserve the exact identity of the uploaded dish\r\n- do not redesign or reinterpret it into another menu\r\n- keep the real ingredients, colors, textures, proportions, and recognizable appearance of the uploaded dish\r\n- restage the food naturally into a refined premium plated presentation inspired by the reference\r\n- if the uploaded dish includes sauce, garnish, or side elements, they may be arranged neatly on the plate only if supported by the uploaded image\r\n- make the food look realistic, premium, appetizing, and professionally photographed\r\n- preserve realistic gloss, moisture, crispness, fibers, sauce detail, and natural shadow depth\r\n- do not oversmooth the food\r\n- do not make it look fake or plastic\r\n\r\nTypography concept:\r\n- replace all existing text in the reference with a completely new Thai typography composition\r\n- use Thai language only for all visible text unless the user explicitly inputs another language\r\n- design the typography from scratch as a custom Thai display type composition, not a normal font overlay\r\n- redesign the letterforms, line breaks, size ratios, spacing, and graphic rhythm based on the exact input words\r\n- adapt the graphic typography composition to the actual length and shape of each Thai phrase\r\n- allow custom letterform styling, stroke contrast, ligatures, overlap, stretching, compression, spacing play, and hierarchy design\r\n- typography should feel editorial, premium, elegant, modern, and bespoke\r\n- the main title should feel like a custom poster wordmark\r\n- the supporting line should feel like a refined secondary type layer\r\n- prioritize correct Thai spelling and readable Thai forms\r\n- the result must look like a fully art-directed Thai typography composition, not stock text\r\n\r\nText content:\r\n- Main text: #[ข้อความหลัก](e59088b4-541b-444a-a017-98be2d7deab6) \r\n- Secondary text: #[ข้อความรอง](8d083256-b096-4ec8-a49f-8c47fc59c0df) \r\n\r\nTypography layout rules:\r\n- place the main Thai title in the upper center area as the dominant typographic element\r\n- place the secondary Thai line below the main title in a smaller but elegant complementary style\r\n- recompute the full typography composition every time based on the exact input text\r\n- do not copy the reference text layout literally\r\n- create a new composition that preserves the same premium poster feeling\r\n- keep the typography visually integrated with the food and negative space\r\n- maintain strong hierarchy between main text, secondary text, and plated dish\r\n\r\nTypography styling direction:\r\n- custom Thai editorial display typography\r\n- luxurious, minimal, refined, and modern\r\n- elegant Thai poster composition\r\n- bespoke type design based on the input words\r\n- main text may be bold, wide, tall, condensed, outlined, inline, contrasted, or stylized as appropriate to the words\r\n- secondary text may be softer, more delicate, more cursive-feeling, or more contrast-driven as appropriate\r\n- keep the typography premium and readable\r\n- use light or warm-white Thai typography tones that suit the dark background\r\n- no cheap effects\r\n- no generic font look\r\n- no random Latin-looking Thai\r\n\r\nLighting and mood requirements:\r\n- match the reference image’s dark fine-dining mood\r\n- strong but controlled light focused on the plated dish\r\n- deep background shadows\r\n- subtle premium highlights on plate, sauce, and cutlery\r\n- overall tone should feel elegant, intimate, luxurious, and restaurant-editorial\r\n\r\nImportant constraints:\r\n- render only the exact text provided in the input fields\r\n- do not add extra text\r\n- do not change spelling\r\n- do not invent subtitles\r\n- remove all original reference text completely\r\n- no watermark\r\n- no logo unless explicitly provided\r\n- no extra dishes\r\n- no unrelated props\r\n- no messy layout\r\n- no distorted food\r\n- no unreadable typography\r\n- no fake Thai glyphs\r\n- no placeholder English text\r\n\r\nStyle direction:\r\npremium Thai fine-dining poster, custom Thai composition typography, elegant editorial restaurant campaign, minimal luxury food advertising, bespoke type-led visual design","model_name":"nano-banana-2","aspect_ratio":"3:4"},"exposed":{}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":360,"y":300}},{"id":"544b9a33-9692-4379-b39a-c0b779bba707","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":750,"y":510}},{"id":"8fb2c46b-e1f4-4c70-ad65-c7f70218ec42","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","config":{"example_image_urls":["https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/flow-assets/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/4034648d-aae9-4eb4-bd7a-7eac3c40cbae.jpg"]},"nodeName":"อาหาร1","required":true,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"อาหาร"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":45,"y":810}},{"id":"e59088b4-541b-444a-a017-98be2d7deab6","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"ข้อความหลัก","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"ข้อความหลัก","isRequired":true,"exampleText":"ข้าวหน้าแซลมอน","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":-270,"y":195}},{"id":"21c01ffd-5ef5-4fb7-bba2-d6b8cd4693be","data":{"label":"Creator Image","accept":"image/*","fileName":"4a181aa1effdd0fb4e276010cd85e4c5.jpg","nodeName":"Creator Image","required":true,"fieldType":"image","uploading":false,"fieldLabel":"your image","previewUrl":"https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/sign/ai-media/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/959d0144-9d82-4f62-9d0e-cd3b0fc4aeae.jpg?token=eyJraWQiOiJzdG9yYWdlLXVybC1zaWduaW5nLWtleV9jM2VkYzBhMy1jMDIyLTQyOTgtODIxMS1mMTc5YTA1ZDUxN2IiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJhaS1tZ