riginal noodle dish with the uploaded food image\r\n- preserve the exact identity of the uploaded dish\r\n- do not redesign or reinterpret it into another menu\r\n- keep the real ingredients, colors, textures, proportions, and recognizable appearance of the uploaded dish\r\n- restage the food naturally into a plated presentation inspired by the reference\r\n- make the dish look realistic, premium, appetizing, and professionally photographed\r\n- preserve realistic gloss, moisture, sauce detail, fibers, crispness, and natural food texture\r\n- do not oversmooth the food\r\n- do not make it look fake or plastic\r\n\r\nLifted-food rule:\r\n- the portion being picked up by the chopsticks must be derived from the uploaded food image only\r\n- the lifted portion must clearly belong to the same uploaded dish on the plate\r\n- if the uploaded dish contains noodles, pasta, shredded strands, melted cheese, or any naturally liftable strands, use those exact food characteristics for the lifted portion\r\n- the lifted strands must visually match the thickness, color, texture, sauce coating, and ingredient identity of the uploaded dish\r\n- if the uploaded dish does not naturally contain long strands, create the most believable lifted bite from the same dish while preserving the same vertical lifted-food storytelling\r\n- do not keep the original reference noodles if the uploaded dish is different\r\n- do not invent unrelated ingredients in the lifted portion\r\n\r\nPlate styling requirements:\r\n- keep the plate presentation abundant and natural\r\n- supporting vegetables, garnish, or side ingredients may appear only if supported by the uploaded food image\r\n- the lifted portion should visibly connect back to the plated dish\r\n- the plated dish and the lifted bite must feel like one continuous serving moment\r\n\r\nHand and chopsticks requirements:\r\n- keep one natural human hand holding chopsticks from the upper-right\r\n- maintain a realistic elegant grip similar to the reference\r\n- hand should look natural, proportionate, and clean\r\n- chopsticks should remain subtle and secondary to the food\r\n- no distorted fingers, wrist, chopsticks, or unnatural hand pose\r\n\r\nLighting and mood requirements:\r\n- match the reference image’s warm dark restaurant mood\r\n- soft directional light on the plate, lifted food, and hand\r\n- rich highlights on glossy or sauced surfaces\r\n- natural shadow depth on the table and background\r\n- shallow depth of field with softly blurred background\r\n- overall tone should feel warm, intimate, appetizing, and premium\r\n\r\nImportant constraints:\r\n- no text, captions, labels, logos, or watermarks unless explicitly provided\r\n- no unrelated props\r\n- no extra dishes\r\n- no fake ingredients not supported by the uploaded food image\r\n- no messy composition\r\n- no collage layout\r\n- no cartoon look\r\n- no distorted plate, food anatomy, hand, or chopsticks\r\n\r\nStyle direction:\r\npremium restaurant food photography, lifted-bite hero shot, warm moody editorial lighting, realistic plated dish, appetizing vertical food composition\n","model_name":"nano-banana-2","aspect_ratio":"3:4"},"exposed":{"prompt":false}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":360,"y":300}},{"id":"544b9a33-9692-4379-b39a-c0b779bba707","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":750,"y":510}},{"id":"8fb2c46b-e1f4-4c70-ad65-c7f70218ec42","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","config":{"example_image_urls":[]},"nodeName":"อาหาร1","required":true,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"อาหาร"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":45,"y":810}},{"id":"21c01ffd-5ef5-4fb7-bba2-d6b8cd4693be","data":{"label":"Creator Image","accept":"image/*","fileName":"914d3780771c4ec04d0fe7b62c878712.jpg","nodeName":"Creator Image","required":true,"fieldType":"image","uploading":false,"fieldLabel":"your image","previewUrl":"https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/sign/ai-media/fb4de7e2-