"creatorAsset":true},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":-60,"y":-615}},{"id":"6bc6dde5-4cf0-4991-98b2-df0a689c05cf","data":{"label":"Banana Pro (Image Gen)","params":{"prompt":"Use two input images.\r\n\r\nImage A = @[ภาพพื้นหลัง](b874700b-e279-4442-99ff-ae642db299ac) \r\nImage B = @[ต้นแบบ](546edfae-325c-486a-9df9-9ef3f906196f) \r\n\r\nImage A is the replaceable background image and the direct edit target.\r\nImage B is the reference image for composition, layout hierarchy, graphic typography style, sticker shape treatment, and overall promotional mood.\r\n\r\nEdit Image A by placing a Thai promotional typography layout directly on top of it.\r\nUse Image B only as a visual reference for layout style and composition structure.\r\nDo not copy the original text from Image B.\r\nDo not keep any old text from Image A or Image B.\r\nGenerate new text based only on the input text variables below.\r\n\r\nCreate a Thai retail promotional poster in a fun, bold, playful sticker-typography style.\r\nThe design should look like a finished fashion retail promotion graphic.\r\nPreserve the background scene, perspective, lighting, and environment of Image A.\r\nFollow the composition idea from Image B: one small title at the top, one large highlighted message across the upper-middle, and one biggest main headline in the lower-middle area.\r\n\r\nText content to render:#[TEXT_TOP](44a6fca9-6d48-48af-977d-67db69618bfa)\r\n- Middle text: #[TEXT_MIDDLE](bc199b00-0d9e-4f10-b1f0-4fdcacfda9ee) \r\n- Main headline: #[TEXT_MAIN](37eb38c6-85db-4fb3-8509-9ac2b73f3122) \r\n\r\nTypography requirements:\r\n- Use Thai font style “MN MINI” for all Thai text.\r\n- If any English text appears, make it visually compatible with MN MINI: rounded, playful, thick, clean, and easy to read.\r\n- All text must look like designed graphic typography, not plain typed text.\r\n\r\nLayout requirements:\r\n\r\n1) Top text #[TEXT_TOP](44a6fca9-6d48-48af-977d-67db69618bfa) \r\n- Place near the top-center area.\r\n- Put it inside a slightly curved or slightly tilted rounded label.\r\n- Use white text on a dark navy-blue shape.\r\n- This should be the smallest text level and act as the campaign header.\r\n\r\n2) Middle text #[TEXT_MIDDLE](bc199b00-0d9e-4f10-b1f0-4fdcacfda9ee) \r\n- Place across the upper-middle area below the top text.\r\n- Use large bold Thai display text.\r\n- Use black or very dark navy lettering.\r\n- Add a thick light-blue sticker-like outline or backing shape.\r\n- Make it wide, energetic, and eye-catching.\r\n\r\n3) Main headline #[TEXT_MAIN](37eb38c6-85db-4fb3-8509-9ac2b73f3122) \r\n- Place in the lower-middle area as the most dominant element.\r\n- Use very large white text.\r\n- Put the text inside or on top of a large organic bubble/cloud-shaped graphic panel.\r\n- The panel should have a dark denim-blue fabric texture.\r\n- Add a light-blue outer stroke or border to separate it clearly from the background.\r\n- This element must feel bold, soft, playful, cute, and highly promotional.\r\n\r\nGraphic styling:\r\n- Main color palette: dark navy blue, denim blue, light blue, white, and black.\r\n- Style direction: sticker typography, bubble typography, playful retail promotion signage.\r\n- Add subtle soft shadows, thick outlines, and a die-cut sticker feeling.\r\n- Optional small doodle strokes or light-blue scribble accents may be added for extra visual energy.\r\n- Keep the final result clean, modern, cute, commercial, and easy to read.\r\n\r\nAdaptive text behavior:\r\n- Automatically adjust font size, line breaks, spacing, graphic shape width, and container proportions based on the input text length.\r\n- If the text is short, enlarge it for stronger impact.\r\n- If the text is long, wrap the text neatly while maintaining readability and strong hierarchy.\r\n- Expand or reduce the supporting sticker shapes naturally to fit the text.\r\n- Maintain balanced composition similar to the structure shown in Image B.\r\n\r\nImage behavior:\r\n- Always use Image A as the actual background image.\r\n- Image A can be replaced freely in each generation.\r\n- Use Image B only as a reference for styling and composition.\r\n- Keep the environment in Image A believable and visually clean.\r\n- Do not drastically change the background unless needed for readability.\r\n\r\nImportant instructions:\r\n- Use Image A as the final background.\r\n- Use Image B as the reference only.\r\n- Remove and replace any existing text overlays.\r\n- Do not include date or period text.\r\n- Do not reuse the original wording from the reference.\r\n- The final output should look like a finished promotional poster ready for use.","model_name":"nano-banana-2","aspect_ratio":"Auto"},"exposed":{}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":300,"y":-255}},{"id":"44a6fca9-6d48-48af-977d-67db69618bfa","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"TEXT_TOP","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"TEXT_TOP","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":-405,"y":-765}},{"id":"bc199b00-0d9e-4f10-b1f0-4fdcacfda9ee","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"TEXT_MIDDLE","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"TEXT_MIDDLE","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":-405,"y":-300}},{"id":"37eb38c6-85db-4fb3-8509-9ac2b73f3122","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"TEXT_MAIN","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"TEXT_MAIN","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":-405,"y":180}},{"id":"86b9a84f-1f63-41dc-b62e-7712e07bf359","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":735,"y":-135}}]},"example_inputs":[],"preview_images":["https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-preview-2030c281-ad52-4b8b-9192-64ec2c778da8-1776682623611-0.jpg?t=1776682624844"],"setup_instructions":"เพิ่มรูปภาพคอนเทนต์ 1 รูป พร้อมรายละเอียดข้อความบนหน้าปก แล้วกดสร้างได้ทันที"},"base_cost":300,"embedding":"[-0.003776