t effect style in a way that feels beautiful, bold, clean, and commercially usable. Effects may include depth, outline, layered shapes, highlights, shadows, graphic framing, or premium decorative styling depending on the requested direction.\r\n\r\nMake the main headline the most eye-catching text element. The price or discount text should also be highly prominent when provided. Sub text should be smaller but still readable. Promo badge text should appear as a short supporting graphic element when provided.\r\n\r\nRespect the requested text colors as closely as possible while keeping all text readable. Use the requested text position and background mood to build a balanced and attractive composition. Keep enough visual separation so the food and the text do not compete too aggressively.\r\n\r\nIf a logo is provided, place it cleanly and appropriately in the composition. Preserve the exact original logo identity from the uploaded file, including its layout, colors, proportions, typography, and icon shape. Do not redesign, recreate, simplify, or alter the logo.\r\n\r\nDo not add unrelated dishes, random extra text, watermarks, or collage clutter. Keep the banner polished, professional, highly realistic, and ready for restaurant marketing use.","model_name":"nano-banana-2","aspect_ratio":"Auto"},"exposed":{"aspect_ratio":true}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":210,"y":180}},{"id":"2afe575a-8046-40f6-8411-45f4898c49dc","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Main headline text:","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"ข้อความหลัก","isRequired":true,"exampleText":"ข้อความหัวเรื่องหลักที่ต้องการให้เด่นที่สุดบนภาพ เช่น เมนูใหม่, ดีลพิเศษ, โปรแรงวันนี้","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":-180,"y":690}},{"id":"700a37a5-13d5-4053-a85e-aee5c96e6e21","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Sub text:","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"ข้อความรอง","isRequired":true,"exampleText":"ข้อความอธิบายเพิ่มเติมใต้หัวข้อหลัก เช่น อร่อยเข้มเต็มคำ หรือ พร้อมเ