ly lower in the frame, leaving clean negative space above for text placement. The pedestal should appear at the bottom of the image as a clear horizontal line. Its surface should feel luxurious — such as marble, leather, or polished metal — with sharp, refined details that enhance the scene without distracting from the product.\n\nUse a studio gradient background that matches the product’s main color and material. Keep the pedestal and background within the same color family, but make them one or two shades lighter or darker than the product so the product stands out clearly.\n\nApply premium studio lighting: a soft key light from the front at an angle, a subtle rim light to define the edges and material shine, and realistic one-directional shadows falling naturally onto the pedestal. Add material-specific highlights depending on whether the product is metal, glass, gemstone, or another reflective surface. Keep the product in sharp focus, with a slightly blurred background for depth.\n\nOverall style: clean, minimalist, luxurious, ultra-realistic product photography, highly detailed, 8K.\n\nNegative constraints: no text, no logo, no watermark, no floating, no levitation, no extra products, no extra hands.","model_name":"nano-banana-pro","aspect_ratio":"3:4"},"exposed":{}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":555,"y":270}},{"id":"a9be62f2-b5c5-47d8-89b4-f91bedc4d701","data":{"label":"Creator Image","accept":"image/*","fileName":"freepik__photo-a-heartshaped-diamond-engagement-ring-with-a__46516.png","nodeName":"Creator Image","required":true,"fieldType":"image","uploading":false,"fieldLabel":"Upload your image","previewUrl":"https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/sign/ai-media/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/4d09c90e-572a-4c69-91dd-60fef01673a1.png?token=eyJraWQiOiJzdG9yYWdlLXVybC1zaWduaW5nLWtleV9jM2VkYzBhMy1jMDIyLTQyOTgtODIxMS1mMTc5YTA1ZDUxN2IiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJhaS1tZWRpYS9mYjRkZTdlMi05ZjZlLTQ1OWItYmIxYi00NjRmNmFlMTRiZWEvNGQw