: ##[Seasonal Theme](c1737a75-be26-418e-8cd1-03dd372a4afc) \r\nAdditional dish details provided by the user: ##[Optional dish details](ac34b952-ffc4-4765-946b-473618fac376) \r\nSeasonal mood requested by the user: ##[Seasonal mood](5d55cea4-adf8-4ebb-9cde-8bccb850995c) \r\nPreferred color direction: ##[Color direction](2c39c903-e2d8-4007-ba44-62cefec232d9) \r\nSeasonal props intensity: ##[Seasonal props intensity](e2396799-e57c-4f80-9306-f4c80d658558) \r\n\r\nTreat the uploaded image, the user-provided dessert name, and the seasonal theme as the source of truth. The final result must still clearly represent this specific seasonal dessert item, not a similar or different dessert. Preserve the original dessert identity, shape, ingredients, proportions, styling logic, and recognizable appearance from the input image.\r\n\r\nDo not redesign, replace, or reinterpret the dessert. Enhance it only into a more polished professional seasonal dessert campaign image while keeping it faithful to the uploaded image and menu name.\r\n\r\nTransform it into a premium seasonal dessert promo shot with a refined café or patisserie feel. Create a visually beautiful, soft, elegant, and appetizing composition that highlights the dessert as the main subject. The final image should feel seasonal, premium, and highly suitable for café promotions, seasonal dessert launches, or festive campaign visuals.\r\n\r\nReflect the requested seasonal theme through delicate seasonal styling, color harmony, elegant background mood, and tasteful decorative elements. Use dessert-appropriate seasonal cues such as seasonal fruits, subtle frosting details, festive garnish, ribbons, floral accents, soft linen, ceramic styling, pastel or festive tones, and refined café table presentation when appropriate. Keep the seasonal styling tasteful and secondary to the dessert.\r\n\r\nUse flattering lighting that enhances cream texture, glaze, fruit freshness, crumbs, chocolate detail, syrup shine, layered structure, and softness. The image should feel polished, charming, premium, and emotionally appealing.\r\n\r\nIf the user requests subtle seasonal props, keep the composition minimal and refined. If the user requests medium or strong seasonal props, increase the visible seasonal atmosphere while preserving a premium dessert-focused presentation.\r\n\r\nDo not add text, logos, watermarks, collage layout, hands, or unrelated desserts. Preserve realism, beauty, and seasonal dessert campaign appeal.","model_name":"nano-banana-pro","aspect_ratio":"Auto"},"exposed":{"aspect_ratio":true}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":330,"y":90}},{"id":"98738615-b50c-41a6-bc04-54fbe3cac92a","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Menu Name","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"อาหารของคุณคือ","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":660,"y":225}},{"id":"5d55cea4-adf8-4ebb-9cde-8bccb850995c","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Seasonal mood","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"อารมณ์ของภาพที่ต้องการ เช่น fresh and bright / cozy and warm / festive and elegant / romantic / playful / premium","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":660,"y":435}},{"id":"c1737a75-be26-418e-8cd1-03dd372a4afc","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Seasonal Theme","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"ธีมที่ต้องการ เช่น Summer / Christmas / New Year / Valentine / Songkran / Autumn / Spring / Mango","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":945,"y":225}},{"id":"2c39c903-e2d8-4007-ba44-62cefec232d9","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Color direction","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"โทนสีของภาพ เช่น ชมพูพาสเทล , แดงและทอง , ฟ้าสงกรานต์ , เขียวมัทฉะ","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":945,"y":435}},{"id":"ac34b952-ffc4-4765-946b-473618fac376","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Optional dish details","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"รายละเอียดเพิ่มเติม เช่น เมนูนี้เป็นแบบร้อนหรือเย็น , เป็น