 the plate only if clearly supported by the uploaded image\r\n- if the uploaded dish does not include certain ingredients, do not add them\r\n- preserve realistic moisture, gloss, freshness, fibers, seeds, sauce texture, and natural surface detail\r\n- make the food look fresh, spicy, vibrant, realistic, and professionally photographed\r\n- do not oversmooth the food\r\n- do not make it look fake, plastic, or overly polished\r\n\r\nLighting and mood requirements:\r\n- match the reference image’s warm rustic food-photography mood\r\n- soft directional lighting with natural highlight falloff\r\n- rich warm brown and green tones\r\n- realistic shadow depth\r\n- shallow depth of field with softly blurred background ingredients\r\n- overall tone should feel homestyle, fresh, premium, and inviting\r\n\r\nStyling constraints:\r\n- keep the visual energy of a styled ingredient-rich food setup\r\n- supporting elements must enhance the hero dish, not distract from it\r\n- non-food props may remain minimal and subtle only if they support the composition naturally\r\n- do not clutter the frame\r\n- keep the image commercially usable and well balanced\r\n\r\nImportant constraints:\r\n- absolutely no text, letters, captions, labels, logos, watermarks, or typography anywhere in the image\r\n- remove any watermark-like artifacts from the final result\r\n- no unrelated props\r\n- no fake ingredients\r\n- no extra dishes not supported by the uploaded image\r\n- no collage layout\r\n- no cartoon look\r\n- no messy composition\r\n- no duplicated ingredients unless naturally justified by the uploaded dish\r\n- no distorted plate, bowl, food anatomy, or table perspective\r\n\r\nStyle direction:\r\npremium Thai food commercial photography, rustic ingredient-rich food styling, warm moody restaurant editorial look, realistic texture, fresh vibrant plating, cinematic appetizing hero shot","model_name":"nano-banana-2","aspect_ratio":"3:4"},"exposed":{"aspect_ratio":true}},"type":"bananaProNod