0-bb1c-35dd4f6bfcd0default-ca54849d-dea0-4e61-ad4c-9813d9d3ac6bref_image","source":"a32f31b8-222d-46a0-bb1c-35dd4f6bfcd0","target":"ca54849d-dea0-4e61-ad4c-9813d9d3ac6b","sourceHandle":"default","targetHandle":"ref_image"}],"nodes":[{"id":"8d083256-b096-4ec8-a49f-8c47fc59c0df","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"ราคา1","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"ราคาจาน1","isRequired":true,"placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":-330,"y":255}},{"id":"ca54849d-dea0-4e61-ad4c-9813d9d3ac6b","data":{"label":"Banana Pro (Image Gen)","params":{"prompt":"Create a premium Japanese-style restaurant menu poster in portrait layout, inspired by bold red-and-white Japanese food advertising design. @@[Creator Image](21c01ffd-5ef5-4fb7-bba2-d6b8cd4693be) \r\n\r\nUse the uploaded food image 1 as the exact reference for Dish 1.@[อาหาร1](8fb2c46b-e1f4-4c70-ad65-c7f70218ec42) \r\nUse the uploaded food image 2 as the exact reference for Dish 2.@[อาหาร2](c93734e5-6703-4646-8207-4a63d6ef5a02) \r\nUse the uploaded logo image as the exact reference for the center logo.@@[โลโก้](a32f31b8-222d-46a0-bb1c-35dd4f6bfcd0) \r\n\r\nThe final poster must preserve the true identity of both dishes from the uploaded images. Do not replace the dishes with different food. Keep the ingredients, shape, color, proportions, plating style, and overall recognizable appearance faithful to the uploaded food images, while upgrading them into a polished commercial poster composition.\r\n\r\nPoster layout:\r\n- Portrait poster\r\n- Strong Japanese restaurant visual identity\r\n- Main color theme: deep red and white\r\n- Top section divided into 3 white sign panels\r\n- Left top panel contains editable headline text\r\n- Center top panel contains a circular Japanese stamp-style logo area with the uploaded logo placed in the middle\r\n- Right top panel contains editable vertical Japanese-style text\r\n- Background is rich red with subtle Japanese-style line art, traditional architecture motifs, and faint cultural illustration details\r\n- Overall look should feel like a modern Japanese restaurant promotion poster, bold, appetizing, clean, and premium\r\n\r\nFood composition:\r\n- Dish 1 placed in the upper-left to mid-left area, slightly larger hero placement\r\n- Dish 2 placed in the lower-right area, balanced against Dish 1\r\n- Both dishes must look like professionally shot food photography with realistic lighting, natural shadows, crisp texture, appetizing highlights, and clean cutout edges integrated smoothly into the poster\r\n- Re-angle and reframe the dishes slightly if needed for better balance, but keep them faithful to the uploaded food references\r\n- Make both dishes look delicious, premium, and commercially usable\r\n- No extra dishes, no additional props unless they support the original dish naturally\r\n\r\nTypography and text rendering:\r\nRender all text exactly as provided by the user. Do not rewrite, shorten, auto-correct, translate, invent, or add extra text.\r\nUse a bold Thai type style inspired by Japanese brush calligraphy for the Thai text.\r\nUse a Japanese brush / restaurant sign style for Japanese text elements.\r\nTypography should feel expressive, premium, slightly hand-painted, and highly legible.\r\nText must be laid out cleanly and beautifully like a restaurant ad poster.\r\n\r\nEditable text fields:\r\nTop-left headline text:#[ซ้าย](f7fea6b7-5f80-442f-83e3-a782af8054f1) \r\nCenter logo text or logo mark: use uploaded logo image\r\nTop-right vertical text:#[ขวา](992baf3b-0039-4c36-89b8-4a1237c0052f) \r\n\r\nDish 1 main title:#[เฮดไลน์1](e59088b4-541b-444a-a017-98be2d7deab6) \nDish 1 price text inside white brush-circle badge:##[ราคา1](8d083256-b096-4ec8-a49f-8c47fc59c0df) \r\n\r\nDish 2 main title:#[เฮดไลน์2](fb26f51a-721f-4d6a-9689-5445015eb3c3)\nDish 2 price text inside white brush-circle badge:#[ราคา2](0fb77303-daae-425b-8dbe-7e77715ea88d) \r\n\r\nPrice badge styling:\r\n- White circular brush-stroke badge\r\n- Rough ink-brush ring effect\r\n- Bold red price text\r\n- One badge near each dish\r\n- Badges must feel hand-painted and premium, matching Japanese restaurant poster style\r\n\r\nLogo styling:\r\n- Center top logo inside a red circular brush-stamp emblem\r\n- Uploaded logo must be clearly visible and centered\r\n- The logo area should feel like a Japanese seal / stamp mark\r\n- Keep it clean, iconic, and balanced with the overall layout\r\n\r\nStyle goals:\r\n- premium Japanese food poster\r\n- strong red-white contrast\r\n- appetizing commercial food photography\r\n- Thai text in Japanese-inspired brush style\r\n- dynamic but clean composition\r\n- realistic lighting and texture\r\n- visually balanced layout\r\n- poster-ready marketing design\r\n\r\nImportant rules:\r\n- Keep exactly 2 dishes only\r\n- Keep the uploaded foods recognizable\r\n- Keep the center logo editable / replaceable from the uploaded logo\r\n- Render only the user-provided text\r\n- Do not generate gibberish text\r\n- Do not add random English or Japanese characters unless explicitly provided in the text inputs\r\n- Do not overcrowd the layout\r\n- Make the final result look like a real professional restaurant promotion poster","model_name":"nano-banana-2","aspect_ratio":"3:4"},"exposed":{}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":420,"y":-330}},{"id":"544b9a33-9692-4379-b39a-c0b779bba707","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":915,"y":-330}},{"id":"8fb2c46b-e1f4-4c70-ad65-c7f70218ec42","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","config":{"example_image_urls":["https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/flow-assets/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/1a790fa7-0181-4054-b607-f70e67e4e798.jpg"]},"nodeName":"อาหาร1","required":true,"fieldType":"image","fieldLabel":"อาหาร1"},"type":"inputNode","position":{"x":-615,"y":600}},{"id":"c93734e5-6703-4646-8207-4a63d6ef5a02","data":{"label":"Image Upload","accept":"image/*","config":{"