picked up, or held naturally by the specified utensil. The utensil must interact with the food in a realistic, appetizing way, as if capturing the perfect bite.\r\n\r\nMake sure the utensil grip and food interaction look natural and believable. The lifted portion should not look artificial, broken, or physically impossible. Show the most appetizing interior and surface details of the food in the lifted portion.\r\n\r\nRespect the serving temperature provided by the user. Only show steam, heat, condensation, frost, chilled cues, or temperature-related visual details when naturally appropriate for that specific menu item and serving condition. If the dish is hot or warm, subtle realistic steam may be shown when suitable. If the dish is cold, iced, chilled, or room temperature, do not add steam or hot-food cues.\r\n\r\nEmphasize rich food texture, realistic detail, shallow depth of field, and irresistible appetite appeal. Highlight qualities such as gloss, sauce, steam, melted cheese, crisp edges, juicy layers, noodles, grains, cream, filling, or freshness depending on the dish. The lifted portion should feel natural, visually satisfying, and true to the original menu item.\r\n\r\nUse premium food-commercial lighting, realistic shadows, and strong focus on the lifted bite. Keep the background soft and secondary so the food remains the clear hero. The final image should feel highly realistic, dramatic, premium, and commercially usable.\r\n\r\nDo not add text, logos, watermarks, collage layout, or unrelated items. Preserve realism and strong macro food appeal.\n","model_name":"nano-banana-pro","aspect_ratio":"Auto"},"exposed":{"aspect_ratio":true}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":255,"y":105}},{"id":"50e9efcb-95e0-4644-81d8-9291ce043983","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Menu Name","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"อาหารของคุณคือ","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":600,"y":225}},{"id":"26e1716f-ffef-4b71-ab27-728bd0e815a4