](ba707b50-a8a0-41d1-9b9e-0e40b8f0e1ca) \r\n\rPreferred Main text position: #[Main text position](3f8cb89d-e9e1-40f6-8b53-2e3e9007a63d) \nSub text: #[Sub text](5717f203-94c6-49c7-9290-c3eaa606eede) \r\nSub text color: #[Sub text color](426b28ac-9012-4d33-96ac-cf2416568049) \r\n\r\nPrice text color: #[Price text color](248a632d-ba26-4c87-8385-b76f7c63d4e5) \r\nPrice badge style: #[Price badge style](495633dd-8e2c-4dcc-873c-363c1ce5e04f) \r\nPrice position: #[Price position](3e643d3f-89eb-4843-a6a6-f738a04920f5) \r\n\r\nPromo badge text: #[Promo badge text](64950a56-dfa3-4da4-be1b-dc9de015e0c2) \r\nPromo badge color: #[Promo badge color](272e4e81-cfbe-4789-81ff-cbd3ed2b357d) \r\n\r\nLogo to display on the image: @[Logo](80ed10d8-ad59-4e93-9e5d-60f1c3048975) \r\nPreferred logo position: #[Logo position](91199de4-2084-4fd5-aa92-40cee34bc9c8) \r\nPreferred logo size: #[Logo size](1600b2cf-574d-4c2b-bf8a-ee0adea859ff) \nPreferred background style: #[Background style](8945b45e-7c9b-42a4-82a2-63c8457b794a) \nTreat the uploaded image and the user-provided dish name as the source of truth. The final result must still clearly represent this specific menu item, not a similar or different dish. Preserve the original dish identity, ingredients, proportions, plating logic, and recognizable appearance from the input image.\r\n\r\nDo not redesign, replace, or reinterpret the dish. Enhance it only into a more polished professional food promotional design while keeping it faithful to the uploaded image and menu name.\r\n\r\nTransform it into a premium menu promo image with clearly integrated price information. Create a clean, appetizing, commercially usable composition where the food remains attractive and prominent, while the menu name, price, optional supporting text, and optional promo badge are placed clearly and beautifully in the layout.\r\n\r\nRender all text exactly as provided by the user. Do not translate, rewrite, shorten, paraphrase, or add extra text. If a currency or price format is provided, follow it exactly. Make the price highly readable and visually important, while still keeping the food as the main visual hero.\r\n\r\nUse clean, bold, readable typography with strong contrast against the background. Respect the requested text colors as closely as possible while keeping all text legible. If a price badge style is provided, reflect that style in a polished and realistic promotional layout. Arrange the composition so the food, the price, and the supporting text feel balanced and easy to read at a glance.\r\n\r\nIf a logo is provided, place it clearly and elegantly in the composition as part of the promotional design. Preserve the exact original logo identity from the uploaded file, including its layout, colors, proportions, typography, icon shape, and brand character. Do not redesign, restyle, simplify, recreate, or alter the logo. Keep the logo clean, readable, and secondary to the food and price.\r\n\r\nIf a background style is provided, reflect it in the composition while keeping the overall image uncluttered and promotion-friendly. If no background style is provided, use a clean, premium, minimal background by default.\r\n\r\nDo not add any extra dishes, unrelated props, watermarks, or collage layout. Keep the final result highly realistic, polished, premium, and ready for restaurant marketing or menu promotion use.","model_name":"nano-banana-2","aspect_ratio":"Auto"},"exposed":{"aspect_ratio":true}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":315,"y":-105}},{"id":"c02659b6-e76d-4f20-a383-a7d0747f70f9","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"[Menu Name]","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"ระบุชื่อเมนูที่อัพโหลด","isRequired":true,"exampleText":"","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":645,"y":285}},{"id":"e20a605c-aa1a-4879-8532-80c47c10c670","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"[Price]","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"ระบุราคาที่ต้องการแสดงบนภาพ","isRequired":true,"exampleText":"เช่น 89, 129 หรือ