 drink details provided by the user: ##[Optional dish details](9e53e5b4-4242-4741-8b00-45a92f61563c) \r\nSeasonal mood requested by the user: ##[Seasonal mood](01aaeacf-4f94-4288-bd7b-5599755f0784) \r\nPreferred color direction: #[Color direction]\r\nSeasonal props intensity: ##[Seasonal props intensity](2277b475-1377-4d40-b645-9ba316e8650f) \r\n\r\n\r\nTreat the uploaded image, the user-provided drink name, and the seasonal theme as the source of truth. The final result must still clearly represent this specific seasonal drink item, not a similar or different beverage. Preserve the original drink identity, cup or glass style, ingredients, color, garnish logic, proportions, and recognizable appearance from the input image.\r\n\r\nDo not redesign, replace, or reinterpret the drink. Enhance it only into a more polished professional seasonal drink campaign image while keeping it faithful to the uploaded image and menu name.\r\n\r\nTransform it into a premium seasonal beverage promo shot with strong café or drink-brand campaign appeal. Create a visually refreshing, attractive, and premium composition that highlights the drink as the main subject. The final image should feel seasonal, highly appetizing, and commercially usable for beverage promotions, café menus, or festive campaigns.\r\n\r\nReflect the requested seasonal theme through suitable beverage styling, color harmony, seasonal garnish, atmospheric background, and tasteful decorative accents. Use drink-appropriate seasonal elements only when naturally appropriate, such as condensation, ice sparkle, steam for hot drinks, citrus, herbs, seasonal fruits, cinnamon, festive stirrers, warm cozy props, snow-like accents, summer freshness, or elegant holiday details depending on the theme. Keep the drink as the clear hero.\r\n\r\nUse lighting that enhances transparency, shine, liquid texture, condensation, foam, cream, layering, glass reflections, or steam depending on the beverage type. Emphasize freshness for cold drinks and warmth for hot drinks. The image should feel crisp, premium, inviting, and campaign-ready.\r\n\r\nIf the user requests subtle seasonal props, keep the styling clean and restrained. If the user requests medium or strong seasonal props, increase the visible seasonal atmosphere while preserving a premium drink-focused presentation.\r\n\r\nDo not add text, logos, watermarks, collage layout, hands, or unrelated food items. Preserve realism and seasonal beverage campaign appeal.","model_name":"nano-banana-pro","aspect_ratio":"Auto"},"exposed":{"aspect_ratio":true}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":345,"y":165}},{"id":"29d7ccbd-4c3f-410d-97e6-e2c45e2693e9","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Menu Name","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"เครื่องดื่มของคุณคือ","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":675,"y":300}},{"id":"077b6c34-6c80-4eae-89c6-e4e65a9863a0","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Seasonal Theme","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"ธีมที่ต้องการ เช่น Summer / Christmas / New Year / Valentine / Songkran / Autumn / Spring / Mango","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":960,"y":300}},{"id":"9e53e5b4-4242-4741-8b00-45a92f61563c","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Optional dish details","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"รายละเอียดเพิ่มเติม เช่น เมนูนี้เป็นแบบร้อนหรือเย็น , เป็นเมนูสไตล์โฮมมี่ อบอุ่น ดูเข้าถึงง่าย","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":1245,"y":300}},{"id":"01aaeacf-4f94-4288-bd7b-5599755f0784","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Seasonal mood","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"อารมณ์ของภาพที่ต้องการ เช่น fresh and bright / cozy and warm / festive and elegant / romantic / playful / premium","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":675,"y":525}},{"id":"811b56c2-6fc8-4e8f-9fd4-e18c8b80166e","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Color direction","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"โทนสีของภาพ เช่น ชมพูพาส