esentation: a close, slightly dynamic, slightly angled hero perspective depending on the dish. Emphasize size, depth, texture, richness, and immediate visual appetite appeal. Keep the image highly realistic, polished, commercially usable, and premium.\r\n\r\nDo not add text, logos, watermarks, extra unrelated dishes, unrealistic garnish, collage layout, or human hands. Avoid changing the food into another menu item. Preserve realism and authentic fast food appeal.","model_name":"nano-banana-pro","aspect_ratio":"Auto"},"exposed":{"aspect_ratio":true}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":225,"y":180}},{"id":"ed77abf9-3981-4d67-8516-bc89e6d1ef0b","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"1","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"เมนูของคุณคืออะไร","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":540,"y":225}},{"id":"72cccbd4-1f07-4717-8b5d-830698c99e91","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"2","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"รายละเอียดเพิ่มเติม เช่น กุ้งชิ้นใหญ่","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":540,"y":435}},{"id":"7f0f5fdb-4e7a-449d-a99c-371e64b79a4e","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":825,"y":135}}]},"example_inputs":[],"preview_images":["https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-preview-2b76df1a-283d-4ba2-8e6e-08de65d09d22-1775741473116-0.jpg?t=1775741473917","https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-preview-2b76df1a-283d-4ba2-8e6e-08de65d09d22-1775741473917-1.jpg?t=1775741474935","https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1b-464f6ae14bea/flow-preview-2b76df1a-283d-4ba2-8e6e-08de65d09d22-1775741474935-2.jpg?t=1775741475677","https://mlbzgtoiozqztoszvkuc.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preset-thumbnails/fb4de7e2-9f6e-459b-bb1