ay on the image: @@[logo Upload](c15ec9a1-6991-4742-ab09-e18d30e5e728) \r\nPreferred logo position: ##[Logo position](2524ccf4-7e97-4e79-b3cf-c14c4760b549) \r\nPreferred logo size: ##[Logo size](6273249c-e30d-40f7-b5ff-4f7260ede7e0) \r\n\r\nTreat the uploaded image and the user-provided dish name as the source of truth. The final result must still clearly represent this specific menu item, not a similar or different dish. Preserve the original dish identity, ingredients, plating logic, and recognizable appearance from the input image.\r\n\r\nDo not redesign, replace, or reinterpret the dish. Keep it faithful to the uploaded image and menu name.\r\n\r\nIf text is provided, place it clearly and beautifully in the composition as part of a premium food promotional design. Render the text exactly as provided by the user. Do not translate, rewrite, shorten, or paraphrase the text. Do not add any extra text.\r\n\r\nUse clean, bold, readable typography with strong contrast against the background. Respect the requested text colors as closely as possible while keeping the text legible. Arrange the composition so the food remains attractive and the text remains easy to read. Leave enough negative space for the text placement when appropriate.\r\n\r\nIf a logo is provided, place it clearly and elegantly in the composition as part of a premium food promotional design. Preserve the exact original logo identity from the uploaded file, including its layout, colors, proportions, typography, icon shape, and brand character. Do not redesign, restyle, simplify, recreate, or alter the logo.\r\n\r\nKeep the logo clean, readable, and secondary to the food. The logo should support the branding without overpowering the main food visuals. Place it in a natural position with appropriate spacing and safe margins from the edges.\r\n\r\nDo not invent a new logo. Use only the uploaded logo file when provided.\r\nKeep the logo sharp, proportionally correct, and visually balanced within the layout.\r\n\r\nWhen no text is provided, keep the image clean with no typography.\r\nWhen text is provided, integrate only the user-provided text and no other wording.\r\nIf no logo is provided, do not add any logo or brand mark.\r\n\r\nMake the final result feel like a polished food promotion banner, not just a plain food photo, when text or logo is provided.","model_name":"nano-banana-2","aspect_ratio":"Auto"},"exposed":{"aspect_ratio":true}},"type":"bananaProNode","position":{"x":315,"y":90}},{"id":"e09a7aff-d81d-4a80-adaa-97a069f55f9e","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Menu Name","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"เมนูของคุณคือ","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":-360,"y":600}},{"id":"3dfb35fb-1492-4cab-b3b4-7c7645f7b7df","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Optional dish details","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"รายละเอียดเพิ่มเติม","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":-360,"y":810}},{"id":"33b503a0-8389-4d98-aff5-1a85c8efc6be","data":{"label":"Output","outputType":"video"},"type":"outputNode","position":{"x":720,"y":90}},{"id":"3da3e3e9-32d1-47b4-ac07-aa0f4325eee1","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Main text","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"ข้อความหลักของคุณ","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":-30,"y":600}},{"id":"2d4e340c-db95-4b35-9933-eef109d9727b","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Main text color","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"สีของข้อความหลัก","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":240,"y":600}},{"id":"32032b16-f7d4-4f1f-b9d9-d192a03a2a31","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Sub text","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"ข้อความย่อยของคุณ","placeholder":"Enter text value..."},"type":"textInputNode","position":{"x":-30,"y":810}},{"id":"5319639e-1419-4656-bd09-c7825270eb29","data":{"label":"Text Input","nodeName":"Sub text color","textValue":"","fieldLabel":"สีของข้อแความย่อย","placeholder":"Enter tex